- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-818">vat number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-818">austrian vat number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-819">vat no.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-819">vat no.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-820">vatno#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-820">vatno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-821">付加価値税番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-821">value added tax number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-822">vat</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-822">austrian vat</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-823">wbst</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-823">mwst</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-824">umsatzsteuernummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-824">umsatzsteuernummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-825">wbstnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-825">mwstnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-826">ust.-identifikationsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-826">ust.-identifikationsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-827">umsatzsteuer-identifikationsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-827">umsatzsteuer-identifikationsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-828">vat identification number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-828">vat identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-829">atu number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-829">atu number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-830">uid number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-830">uid number</span></span>


## <a name="azure-documentdb-auth-key"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-831">Azure DocumentDB 認証キー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-831">Azure DocumentDB auth key</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-832">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-832">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-833">文字列 "DocumentDb" の後に、次のパターンでアウトラインで示されている文字と文字列を指定します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-833">The string "DocumentDb" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-834">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-834">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-835">文字列 "DocumentDb"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-835">The string "DocumentDb"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-836">3 ~ 200 文字の小文字または大文字、数字、記号、特殊文字、またはスペースの任意の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-836">Any combination of between 3-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-837">A greater than symbol (>), an equal sign (=), a quotation mark ("), or an apostrophe (')</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-837">A greater than symbol (>), an equal sign (=), a quotation mark ("), or an apostrophe (')</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-838">86 文字の小文字または大文字、数字、スラッシュ (/)、またはプラス記号 (+) の任意の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-838">Any combination of 86 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-839">2 つの等号 (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-839">Two equal signs (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-840">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-840">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-841">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-841">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-842">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-842">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-843">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-843">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-844">パターンに一CEP_Regex_AzureDocumentDBAuthKeyコンテンツを検索する正規表現。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-844">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureDocumentDBAuthKey finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-845">パターンに一CEP_CommonExampleKeywordsコンテンツが見つからない正規表現。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-845">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Azure Document DB Auth Key -->
<Entity id="0f587d92-eb28-44a9-bd1c-90f2892b47aa" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureDocumentDBAuthKey" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
          </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-846">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-846">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="cep_commonexamplekeywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-847">CEP_CommonExampleKeywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-847">CEP_CommonExampleKeywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-848">(技術的には、この機密情報の種類は、キーワード リストではなく正規表現を使用してこれらのキーワードを識別します)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-848">(Technically, this sensitive information type identifies these keywords by using a regular expression, not a keyword list.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-849">contoso</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-849">contoso</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-850">fabrikam</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-850">fabrikam</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-851">northwind</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-851">northwind</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-852">sandbox</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-852">sandbox</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-853">onebox</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-853">onebox</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-854">localhost</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-854">localhost</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-855">127.0.0.1</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-855">127.0.0.1</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-856">testacs。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-856">testacs.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-857">com</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-857">com</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-858">s-int.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-858">s-int.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-859">net</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-859">net</span></span>

## <a name="azure-iaas-database-connection-string-and-azure-sql-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-860">Azure IAAS データベース接続文字列と Azure SQL接続文字列</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-860">Azure IAAS database connection string and Azure SQL connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-861">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-861">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-862">文字列 "Server"、"server"、または "data source" の後に、文字列 "cloudapp.azure" を含む、以下のパターンで概説されている文字と文字列が続きます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-862">The string "Server", "server", or "data source" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the string "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-863">com" または "cloudapp.azure" です。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-863">com" or "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-864">net" または "database.windows.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-864">net" or "database.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-865">net"、および文字列 "Password" または "password" または "pwd" です。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-865">net", and the string "Password" or "password" or "pwd".</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-866">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-866">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-867">文字列 "Server"、"server"、または "data source"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-867">the string "Server", "server", or "data source"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-868">0 から 2 文字の空白文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-868">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-869">等号 (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-869">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-870">0 から 2 文字の空白文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-870">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-871">1 ~ 200 文字の小文字または大文字、数字、記号、特殊文字、またはスペースの任意の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-871">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-872">文字列 "cloudapp.azure。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-872">The string "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-873">com"、"cloudapp.azure。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-873">com", "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-874">net"、または "database.windows.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-874">net", or "database.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-875">net"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-875">net"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-876">1 ~ 300 文字の小文字または大文字、数字、記号、特殊文字、またはスペースの任意の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-876">any combination of between 1-300 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-877">文字列 "Password"、"password"、または "pwd"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-877">the string "Password", "password", or "pwd"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-878">0 から 2 文字の空白文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-878">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-879">等号 (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-879">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-880">0 から 2 文字の空白文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-880">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-881">セミコロンではない 1 つ以上の文字 (;)、引用符 (")、またはアポストロフィ (')</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-881">one or more characters that aren't a semicolon (;), quotation mark ("), or apostrophe (')</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-882">セミコロン (;)、引用符 (")、またはアポストロフィ (')</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-882">a semicolon (;), quotation mark ("), or apostrophe (')</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-883">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-883">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-884">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-884">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-885">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-885">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-886">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-886">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-887">パターンに一CEP_Regex_AzureConnectionStringコンテンツを検索する正規表現。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-887">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-888">パターンに一CEP_CommonExampleKeywordsコンテンツが見つからない正規表現。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-888">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure IAAS Database Connection String and Azure SQL Connection String-->
<Entity id="ce1a126d-186f-4700-8c0c-486157b953fd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="azure-iot-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-903">Azure IoT 接続文字列</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-903">Azure IoT connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-904">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-904">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-905">文字列 "HostName" の後に、次のパターンでアウトラインで示されている文字と文字列 ("azure-devices" という文字列を含む)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-905">The string "HostName" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the strings "azure-devices.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-906">net" および "SharedAccessKey"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-906">net" and "SharedAccessKey".</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-907">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-907">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-908">文字列 "HostName"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-908">the string "HostName"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-909">0 から 2 文字の空白文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-909">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-910">等号 (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-910">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-911">0 から 2 文字の空白文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-911">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-912">1 ~ 200 文字の小文字または大文字、数字、記号、特殊文字、またはスペースの任意の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-912">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-913">文字列 "azure-devices"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-913">the string "azure-devices.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-914">net"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-914">net"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-915">1 ~ 200 文字の小文字または大文字、数字、記号、特殊文字、またはスペースの任意の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-915">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-916">文字列 "SharedAccessKey"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-916">the string "SharedAccessKey"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-917">0 から 2 文字の空白文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-917">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-918">等号 (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-918">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-919">0 から 2 文字の空白文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-919">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-920">43 文字の小文字または大文字、数字、スラッシュ (/)、またはプラス記号 (+) の任意の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-920">any combination of 43 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-921">等号 (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-921">an equal sign (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-922">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-922">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-923">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-923">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-924">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-924">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-925">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-925">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-926">パターンに一CEP_Regex_AzureIoTConnectionStringコンテンツを検索する正規表現。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-926">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureIoTConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-927">パターンに一CEP_CommonExampleKeywordsコンテンツが見つからない正規表現。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-927">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure IoT Connection String-->
<Entity id="0b34bec3-d5d6-4974-b7b0-dcdb5c90c29d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureIoTConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="azure-publish-setting-password"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-942">Azure 発行設定パスワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-942">Azure publish setting password</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-943">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-943">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-944">文字列 "userqpd=" の後に英数字の文字列を指定します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-944">The string "userpwd=" followed by an alphanumeric string.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-945">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-945">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-946">文字列 "userqpd="</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-946">the string "userpwd="</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-947">60 桁の小文字または数字の任意の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-947">any combination of 60 lowercase letters or digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-948">引用符 (")</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-948">a quotation mark (")</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-949">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-949">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-950">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-950">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-951">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-951">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-952">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-952">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-953">パターンに一CEP_Regex_AzurePublishSettingPasswordsコンテンツを検索する正規表現。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-953">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzurePublishSettingPasswords finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-954">パターンに一CEP_CommonExampleKeywordsコンテンツが見つからない正規表現。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-954">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>


```xml
<!--Azure Publish Setting Password-->
<Entity id="75f4cc8a-a68e-49e5-89ce-fa8f03d286a5" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
       <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzurePublishSettingPasswords" />
       <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
           <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
       </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="azure-redis-cache-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-969">Azure Redis キャッシュ接続文字列</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-969">Azure Redis cache connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-970">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-970">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-971">文字列 "redis.cache.windows。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-971">The string "redis.cache.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-972">net" の後に、文字列 "password" または "pwd" を含む、以下のパターンでアウトラインで示されている文字と文字列が続きます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-972">net" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the string "password" or "pwd".</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-973">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-973">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-974">文字列 "redis.cache.windows。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-974">the string "redis.cache.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-975">net"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-975">net"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-976">1 ~ 200 文字の小文字または大文字、数字、記号、特殊文字、またはスペースの任意の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-976">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-977">文字列 "password" または "pwd"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-977">the string "password" or "pwd"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-978">0 から 2 文字の空白文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-978">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-979">等号 (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-979">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-980">0 から 2 文字の空白文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-980">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-981">小文字または大文字、数字、スラッシュ (/)、またはプラス記号 (+) の 43 文字の任意の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-981">any combination of 43 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-982">等号 (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-982">an equal sign (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-983">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-983">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-984">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-984">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-985">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-985">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-986">DLP ポリシーは、抽出した約 300 文字が次の条件に該当することを検出した場合に、85% の確証を持ってそれがこの種類の機密情報であると特定します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-986">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-987">パターンに一CEP_Regex_AzureRedisCacheConnectionStringコンテンツを検索する正規表現。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-987">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureRedisCacheConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-988">パターンに一CEP_CommonExampleKeywordsコンテンツが見つからない正規表現。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-988">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure Redis Cache Connection String-->
<Entity id="095a7e6c-efd8-46d5-af7b-5298d53a49fc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureRedisCacheConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="azure-sas"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1003">Azure SAS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1003">Azure SAS</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1004">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1004">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1005">文字列 "sig" の後に、次のパターンでアウトラインで示されている文字と文字列を指定します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1005">The string "sig" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1006">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1006">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1007">文字列 "sig"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1007">the string "sig"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1008">0 から 2 文字の空白文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1008">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1009">等号 (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1009">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1010">0 から 2 文字の空白文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1010">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1011">43 ~ 53 文字の任意の組み合わせで、小文字または大文字、数字、またはパーセント記号 (%)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1011">any combination of between 43-53 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, or the percent sign (%)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1012">文字列 "%3d"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1012">the string "%3d"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1013">小文字または大文字ではない文字、数字、またはパーセント記号 (%)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1013">any character that isn't a lower- or uppercase letter, digit, or percent sign (%)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1014">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1014">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1015">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1015">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1016">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1016">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1017">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1017">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1018">パターンに一CEP_Regex_AzureSASコンテンツを検索する正規表現。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1018">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureSAS finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure SAS-->
<Entity id="4d235014-e564-47f4-a6fb-6ebb4a826834" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureSAS" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="azure-service-bus-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1019">Azure サービス バス接続文字列</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1019">Azure service bus connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1020">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1020">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1021">文字列 "EndPoint" の後に、文字列 "servicebus.windows" を含む、以下のパターンでアウトラインで示されている文字と文字列が続きます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1021">The string "EndPoint" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the strings "servicebus.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1022">net" および "SharedAccesKey"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1022">net" and "SharedAccesKey".</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1023">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1023">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1024">文字列 "EndPoint"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1024">the string "EndPoint"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1025">0 から 2 文字の空白文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1025">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1026">等号 (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1026">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1027">0 から 2 文字の空白文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1027">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1028">1 ~ 200 文字の小文字または大文字、数字、記号、特殊文字、またはスペースの任意の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1028">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1029">文字列 "servicebus.windows。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1029">the string "servicebus.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1030">net"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1030">net"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1031">1 ~ 200 文字の小文字または大文字、数字、記号、特殊文字、またはスペースの任意の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1031">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1032">文字列 "SharedAccessKey"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1032">the string "SharedAccessKey"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1033">0 から 2 文字の空白文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1033">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1034">等号 (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1034">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1035">0 から 2 文字の空白文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1035">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1036">小文字または大文字、数字、スラッシュ (/)、またはプラス記号 (+) の 43 文字の任意の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1036">any combination of 43 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1037">等号 (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1037">an equal sign (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1038">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1038">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1039">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1039">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1040">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1040">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1041">DLP ポリシーは、抽出した約 300 文字が次の条件に該当することを検出した場合に、85% の確証を持ってそれがこの種類の機密情報であると特定します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1041">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1042">パターンに一CEP_Regex_AzureServiceBusConnectionStringコンテンツを検索する正規表現。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1042">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureServiceBusConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1043">パターンに一CEP_CommonExampleKeywordsコンテンツが見つからない正規表現。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1043">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure Service Bus Connection String-->
<Entity id="b9a6578f-a83f-4fcd-bf44-2130bae49a6f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureServiceBusConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="azure-storage-account-key"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1058">Azure ストレージ アカウント キー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1058">Azure storage account key</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1059">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1059">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1060">文字列 "DefaultEndpointsProtocol" の後に、文字列 "AccountKey" を含む、以下のパターンでアウトラインで示されている文字と文字列が続きます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1060">The string "DefaultEndpointsProtocol" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the string "AccountKey".</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1061">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1061">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1062">文字列 "DefaultEndpointsProtocol"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1062">the string "DefaultEndpointsProtocol"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1063">0 から 2 文字の空白文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1063">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1064">等号 (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1064">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1065">0 から 2 文字の空白文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1065">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1066">1 ~ 200 文字の小文字または大文字、数字、記号、特殊文字、またはスペースの任意の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1066">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1067">文字列 "AccountKey"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1067">the string "AccountKey"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1068">0 から 2 文字の空白文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1068">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1069">等号 (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1069">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1070">0 から 2 文字の空白文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1070">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1071">小文字または大文字、数字、スラッシュ (/)、またはプラス記号 (+) である 86 文字の任意の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1071">any combination of 86 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1072">2 つの等号 (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1072">two equal signs (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1073">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1073">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1074">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1074">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1075">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1075">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1076">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1076">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1077">パターンに一CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKeyコンテンツを検索する正規表現。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1077">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKey finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1078">パターンに一CEP_AzureEmulatorStorageAccountFilterコンテンツが見つからない正規表現。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1078">The regular expression CEP_AzureEmulatorStorageAccountFilter doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1079">パターンに一CEP_CommonExampleKeywordsコンテンツが見つからない正規表現。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1079">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure Storage Account Key-->
<Entity id="c7bc98e8-551a-4c35-a92d-d2c8cda714a7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKey" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_AzureEmulatorStorageAccountFilter" />
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1080">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1080">Keywords</span></span>

## <a name="azure-storage-account-key-generic"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1097">Azure Storage アカウント キー (汎用)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1097">Azure Storage account key (generic)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1098">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1098">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1099">86 文字の小文字または大文字、数字、スラッシュ (/)、またはプラス記号 (+) の任意の組み合わせ。前または後に、以下のパターンでアウトラインで示される文字が続きます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1099">Any combination of 86 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, the forward slash (/), or plus sign (+), preceded or followed by the characters outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1100">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1100">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1101">0 から大きい記号 (>)、アポストロフィ (')、等号 (=)、引用符 (")、または数値記号 (#)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1101">zero to one of the greater than symbol (>), apostrophe ('), equal sign (=), quotation mark ("), or number sign (#)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1102">小文字または大文字、数字、スラッシュ (/)、またはプラス記号 (+) の 86 文字の任意の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1102">any combination of 86 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, the forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1103">2 つの等号 (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1103">two equal signs (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1104">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1104">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1105">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1105">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1106">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1106">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1107">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1107">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1108">パターンに一CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKeyGenericコンテンツを検索する正規表現。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1108">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKeyGeneric finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure Storage Account Key (Generic)-->
<Entity id="7ff41bd0-5419-4523-91d6-383b3a37f084" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKeyGeneric" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
## <a name="belgium-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1109">ベルギーの運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1109">Belgium driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1110">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1110">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1111">スペースと区切り記号のない 10 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1111">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1112">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1112">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1113">10 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1113">10 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1114">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1114">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1115">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1115">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1116">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1116">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1117">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1117">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1118">正規表現は、  `Regex_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1118">The regular expression  `Regex_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1119">キーワードが検出 `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1119">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>
    
```xml
      <!-- Belgium Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="d89fd329-9324-433c-b687-2c37bd5166f3" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="belgium-national-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1252">ベルギーの国民番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1252">Belgium national number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1253">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1253">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1254">11 桁の数字とオプションの区切り文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1254">11 digits plus optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1255">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1255">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1256">11 の数字と区切り文字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1256">11 digits plus delimiters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1257">YY 形式の 6 桁の数字と 2 つのオプションのピリオド。MM.DDの日付</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1257">six digits and two optional periods in the format YY.MM.DD for date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1258">ドット、ダッシュ、スペースの区切り記号 (省略可能)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1258">An optional delimiter from dot, dash, space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1259">3 桁の連続する数字 (男性の場合は奇数、女性の場合も)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1259">three sequential digits (odd for males, even for females)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1260">ドット、ダッシュ、スペースの区切り記号 (省略可能)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1260">An optional delimiter from dot, dash, space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1261">2 桁のチェック ディジット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1261">two check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1262">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1262">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1263">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1263">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1264">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1264">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1265">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1265">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1266">この関数はFunc_belgium_national_numberパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1266">The function Func_belgium_national_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1267">検索されたKeyword_belgium_national_number検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1267">A keyword from Keyword_belgium_national_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1268">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1268">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1269">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたという信頼性が低い。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1269">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1270">この関数はFunc_belgium_national_numberパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1270">The function Func_belgium_national_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1271">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1271">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Belgium National Number -->
       <Entity id="fb969c9e-0fd1-4b18-8091-a2123c5e6a54" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_national_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_belgium_national_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_national_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="belgium-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1330">ベルギーのパスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1330">Belgium passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1331">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1331">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1332">2 桁の文字の後に 6 桁の数字 (スペースまたは区切り記号なし)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1332">two letters followed by six digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1333">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1333">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1334">2 桁の文字、その後に 6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1334">two letters and followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1335">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1335">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1336">該当なし</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1336">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1337">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1337">Definition</span></span>

 <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1338">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1338">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1339">正規表現は、  `Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1339">The regular expression  `Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1340">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1340">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1341">正規表現は、DD MM YY という形式の日付を検索するか、検索 `Regex_eu_passport_date2` されたキーワードを `Keywords_eu_passport_date` `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` 検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1341">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date2` finds date in the format DD MM YY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` or `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1342">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1342">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1343">正規表現は、  `Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1343">The regular expression  `Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1344">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1344">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
      <!-- Belgium Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="d7b1315b-21ca-4774-a32a-596010ff78fd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date2" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

## <a name="belgium-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1371">ベルギーの付加価値税番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1371">Belgium value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1372">この機密情報の種類は、次の場合にのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1372">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1373">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1373">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1374">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1374">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1375">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1375">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1376">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1376">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1377">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1377">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1378">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1378">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1379">12 文字の英数字パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1379">12-character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1380">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1380">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1381">12 文字の英数字のパターン:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1381">12-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1382">文字 B または b</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1382">a letter B or b</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1383">E または e の文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1383">a letter E or e</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1384">0 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1384">a digit 0</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1385">1 ~ 9 の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1385">a digit from 1 to 9</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1386">オプションのドットまたはハイフンまたはスペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1386">an optional dot or Hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1387">4 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1387">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1388">オプションのドットまたはハイフンまたはスペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1388">an optional dot or Hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1389">4 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1389">four digits</span></span>


### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1390">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1390">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1391">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1391">Yes</span></span>


### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1392">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1392">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1393">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1393">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1394">この関数はFunc_belgium_value_added_tax_numberパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1394">The function Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1395">検索されたKeywords_belgium_value_added_tax_number検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1395">A keyword from Keywords_belgium_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1396">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1396">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1397">この関数はFunc_belgium_value_added_tax_numberパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1397">The function Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Belgium Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="85b5b3c3-f2de-4ae8-ac46-fd3cb38bf9ed" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
    </Version>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1403">numéro t.v.a</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1403">numéro t.v.a</span></span>

## <a name="brazil-cpf-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1409">ブラジルの CPF 番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1409">Brazil CPF number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1410">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1410">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1411">書式設定ありまたは書式設定なしのチェック ディジットを含む 11 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1411">11 digits that include a check digit and can be formatted or unformatted</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1412">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1412">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1413">書式設定:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1413">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1414">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1414">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1415">ピリオド</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1415">a period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1416">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1416">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1417">ピリオド</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1417">a period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1418">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1418">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1419">ハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1419">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1420">チェック ディジットの 2 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1420">two digits that are check digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1421">書式設定されていない場合:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1421">Unformatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1422">11 桁の数字 (最後の 2 桁はチェック ディジット)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1422">11 digits where the last two digits are check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1423">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1423">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1424">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1424">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1425">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1425">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1426">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1426">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1427">この関数はFunc_brazil_cpfパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1427">The function Func_brazil_cpf finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1428">検索されたKeyword_brazil_cpf検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1428">A keyword from Keyword_brazil_cpf is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1429">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1429">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1430">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1430">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1431">この関数はFunc_brazil_cpfパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1431">The function Func_brazil_cpf finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1432">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1432">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Brazil CPF Number -->
<Entity id="78e09124-f2c3-4656-b32a-c1a132cd2711" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cpf"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_brazil_cpf"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cpf"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_brazil_cpf"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1434">Keyword_brazil_cpf</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1434">Keyword_brazil_cpf</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1435">CPF</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1435">CPF</span></span>

## <a name="brazil-legal-entity-number-cnpj"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1444">ブラジルの法人番号 (CNPJ)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1444">Brazil legal entity number (CNPJ)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1445">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1445">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1446">登録番号、枝番号、チェック ディジット、および区切り文字を含む 14 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1446">14 digits that include a registration number, branch number, and check digits, plus delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1447">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1447">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1448">14 桁の数字と区切り文字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1448">14 digits, plus delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1449">2 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1449">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1450">ピリオド</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1450">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1451">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1451">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1452">ピリオド</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1452">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1453">3 桁の数字 (この最初の 8 桁は登録番号)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1453">three digits (these first eight digits are the registration number)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1454">スラッシュ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1454">a forward slash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1455">4 桁の分岐番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1455">four-digit branch number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1456">ハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1456">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1457">チェック ディジットの 2 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1457">two digits that are check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1458">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1458">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1459">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1459">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1460">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1460">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1461">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1461">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1462">この関数はFunc_brazil_cnpjパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1462">The function Func_brazil_cnpj finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1463">検索されたKeyword_brazil_cnpj検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1463">A keyword from Keyword_brazil_cnpj is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1464">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1464">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1465">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1465">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1466">この関数はFunc_brazil_cnpjパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1466">The function Func_brazil_cnpj finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1467">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1467">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Brazil Legal Entity Number (CNPJ) -->
<Entity id="9b58b5cd-5e90-4df6-b34f-1ebcc88ceae4" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cnpj"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_brazil_cnpj"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cnpj"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1478">Business</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1478">Business</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1479">Company</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1479">Company</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1480">CNPJ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1480">CNPJ</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1481">Cadastro Nacional da Pessoa Jurídica</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1481">Cadastro Nacional da Pessoa Jurídica</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1482">Cadastro Geral de Contribuintes</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1482">Cadastro Geral de Contribuintes</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1485">Pessoas jurídicas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1485">Pessoas jurídicas</span></span>

## <a name="brazil-national-identification-card-rg"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1489">ブラジルの国民識別カード (RG)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1489">Brazil national identification card (RG)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1490">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1490">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1491">Registro Geral (旧形式): 9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1491">Registro Geral (old format): Nine digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1492">Registro de Identidade (RIC) (新しい形式): 11 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1492">Registro de Identidade (RIC) (new format): 11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1493">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1493">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1494">Registro Geral (従来の形式):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1494">Registro Geral (old format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1495">2 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1495">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1496">ピリオド</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1496">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1497">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1497">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1498">ピリオド</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1498">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1499">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1499">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1500">ハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1500">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1501">チェック ディジットである 1 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1501">one digit that is a check digit</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1502">Registro de Identidade (RIC) (新しい形式):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1502">Registro de Identidade (RIC) (new format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1503">10 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1503">10 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1504">ハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1504">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1505">チェック ディジットである 1 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1505">one digit that is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1506">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1506">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1507">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1507">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1508">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1508">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1509">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1509">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1510">この関数はFunc_brazil_rgパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1510">The function Func_brazil_rg finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1511">検索されたKeyword_brazil_rg検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1511">A keyword from Keyword_brazil_rg is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1512">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1512">The checksum passes.</span></span>


```xml
      <!-- Brazil National ID Card (RG) -->
      <Entity id="486de900-db70-41b3-a886-abdf25af119c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_rg" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_brazil_rg" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1513">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1513">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_brazil_rg"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1514">Keyword_brazil_rg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1514">Keyword_brazil_rg</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1515">Cédula de identidade</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1515">Cédula de identidade</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1516">Identity card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1516">identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1517">national id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1517">national id</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1518">número de rregistro</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1518">número de rregistro</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1519">registro de Iidentidade</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1519">registro de Iidentidade</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1520">registro geral</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1520">registro geral</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1521">RG (このキーワードでは大文字と小文字が区別されます)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1521">RG (this keyword is case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1522">RIC (このキーワードでは大文字と小文字が区別されます)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1522">RIC (this keyword is case-sensitive)</span></span> 


## <a name="bulgaria-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1523">ブルガリアの運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1523">Bulgaria driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1524">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1524">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1525">スペースと区切り記号のない 9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1525">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1526">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1526">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1527">9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1527">nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1528">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1528">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1529">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1529">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1530">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1530">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1531">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1531">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1532">正規表現は、  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1532">The regular expression  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1533">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1533">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Bulgaria Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="66d39258-94c2-43b2-804b-aa312258e54b" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>    
```
