- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1659">шофьорски книжки</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1659">шофьорски книжки</span></span>

## <a name="bulgaria-uniform-civil-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1660">ブルガリアの均一な市民番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1660">Bulgaria uniform civil number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1661">この機密情報の種類は、次の場合にのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1661">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1662">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1662">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1663">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1663">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1664">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1664">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1665">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1665">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1666">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1666">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1667">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1667">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1668">スペースと区切り記号のない 10 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1668">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1669">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1669">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1670">スペースと区切り記号のない 10 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1670">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1671">生年月日 (YYMMDD) に対応する 6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1671">six digits that correspond to the birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1672">出生順に対応する 2 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1672">two digits that correspond to the birth order</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1673">性別に対応する 1 桁の数字: 男性の偶数桁と女性の奇数桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1673">one digit that corresponds to gender: An even digit for male and an odd digit for female</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1674">1 桁のチェック ディジット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1674">one check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1675">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1675">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1676">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1676">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1677">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1677">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1678">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1678">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1679">この関数は  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` 、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1679">The function  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1680">キーワードを  `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` 検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1680">A keyword from  `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1681">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1681">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1682">この関数は  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` 、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1682">The function  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Bulgaria Uniform Civil Number -->
      <Entity id="100d58b1-0a35-4fb1-aa89-e4a86fb53fcc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="bulgaria-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1727">ブルガリアのパスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1727">Bulgaria passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1728">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1728">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1729">スペースと区切り記号のない 9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1729">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1730">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1730">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1731">9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1731">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1732">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1732">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1733">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1733">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1734">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1734">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1735">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1735">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1736">正規表現は、  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1736">The regular expression  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1737">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1737">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1738">正規表現が `Regex_eu_passport_date1` DD.MM.YYYY の形式で日付を検出するか、キーワードを `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 検出した</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1738">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1739">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1739">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1740">正規表現は、  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1740">The regular expression  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1741">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1741">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
      <!-- Bulgaria Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="f7172b82-c588-4216-845e-4e54e397f29a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1742">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1742">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1746">passportid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1746">passportid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1747">passports</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1747">passports</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1748">passportno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1748">passportno</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1751">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1751">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1752">passportnumbers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1752">passportnumbers</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1753">パスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1753">passport numbers</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1754">Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1754">Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1755">номер на паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1755">номер на паспорта</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1756">номер на паспорт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1756">номер на паспорт</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1757">паспортいいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1757">паспорт №</span></span>

## <a name="canada-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1761">カナダの銀行口座番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1761">Canada bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1762">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1762">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1763">7 桁または 12 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1763">7 or 12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1764">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1764">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1765">カナダの銀行口座番号は 7 桁または 12 桁です。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1765">A Canada Bank Account Number is 7 or 12 digits.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1766">カナダの銀行口座転送番号は次のとおりです。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1766">A Canada bank account transit number is:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1767">5 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1767">five digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1768">ハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1768">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1769">3 桁の数字 OR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1769">three digits OR</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1770">ゼロ "0"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1770">a zero "0"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1771">8 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1771">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1772">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1772">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1773">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1773">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1774">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1774">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1775">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1775">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1776">正規表現 Regex_canada_bank_account_number がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1776">The regular expression Regex_canada_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1777">Keyword_canada_bank_account_number のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1777">A keyword from Keyword_canada_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1778">正規表現 Regex_canada_bank_account_transit_number がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1778">The regular expression Regex_canada_bank_account_transit_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1779">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1779">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1780">正規表現 Regex_canada_bank_account_number がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1780">The regular expression Regex_canada_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1781">Keyword_canada_bank_account_number のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1781">A keyword from Keyword_canada_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="552e814c-cb50-4d94-bbaa-bb1d1ffb34de" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Regex_canada_bank_account_transit_number" />
   </Pattern>
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_bank_account_number" />
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1805">カナダの運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1805">Canada driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1806">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1806">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1807">州によって異なります</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1807">Varies by province</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1808">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1808">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1809">アルバータ州、ブリティッシュ コロンビア州、マニトバ州、ニュー ブランズウィック州、ニューファンドランド・ラブラドール州、ノバスコシア州、オンタリオ州、プリンス エドワード アイランド州、ケベック州、およびサスカチュワン州の各種パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1809">Various patterns covering Alberta, British Columbia, Manitoba, New Brunswick, Newfoundland/Labrador, Nova Scotia, Ontario, Prince Edward Island, Quebec, and Saskatchewan</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1810">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1810">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1811">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1811">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1812">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1812">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1813">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1813">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1814">関数 Func_[province_name]_drivers_license_number がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1814">The function Func_[province_name]_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1815">Keyword_[province_name]_drivers_license_name のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1815">A keyword from Keyword_[province_name]_drivers_license_name is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1816">Keyword_canada_drivers_license のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1816">A keyword from Keyword_canada_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Driver's License Number -->
    <Entity id="37186abb-8e48-4800-ad3c-e3d1610b3db0" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_alberta_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_alberta_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_british_columbia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_british_columbia_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_manitoba_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_manitoba_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_brunswick_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_new_brunswick_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_newfoundland_labrador_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_newfoundland_labrador_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_nova_scotia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_nova_scotia_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_ontario_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ontario_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_prince_edward_island_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_prince_edward_island_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_quebec_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_quebec_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_saskatchewan_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_saskatchewan_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-health-service-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1952">カナダの医療サービス番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1952">Canada health service number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1953">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1953">Format</span></span>

 <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1954">10 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1954">10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1955">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1955">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1956">10 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1956">10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1957">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1957">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1958">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1958">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1959">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1959">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1960">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1960">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1961">正規表現 Regex_canada_health_service_number がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1961">The regular expression Regex_canada_health_service_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1962">Keyword_canada_health_service_number のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1962">A keyword from Keyword_canada_health_service_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Health Service Number -->
<Entity id="59c0bf39-7fab-482c-af25-00faa4384c94" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_health_service_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_health_service_number" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1963">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1963">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_canada_health_service_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1964">Keyword_canada_health_service_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1964">Keyword_canada_health_service_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1965">personal health number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1965">personal health number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1966">patient information</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1966">patient information</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1967">health services</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1967">health services</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1968">speciality services</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1968">speciality services</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1969">automobile accident</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1969">automobile accident</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1970">patient hospital</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1970">patient hospital</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1971">ist</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1971">psychiatrist</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1972">workers compensation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1972">workers compensation</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1973">disability</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1973">disability</span></span>

      
## <a name="canada-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1974">カナダのパスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1974">Canada passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1975">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1975">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1976">2 桁の大文字と 6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1976">two uppercase letters followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1977">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1977">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1978">2 桁の大文字と 6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1978">two uppercase letters followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1979">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1979">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1980">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1980">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1981">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1981">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1982">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1982">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1983">正規表現 Regex_canada_passport_number がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1983">The regular expression Regex_canada_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-1984">検索または検索Keyword_canada_passport_numberキーワードKeyword_passport検出されました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-1984">A keyword from Keyword_canada_passport_number or Keyword_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml 
<!-- Canada Passport Number -->

```

## <a name="canada-personal-health-identification-number-phin"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2014">カナダの個人健康識別番号 (PHIN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2014">Canada personal health identification number (PHIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2015">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2015">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2016">9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2016">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2017">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2017">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2018">9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2018">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2019">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2019">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2020">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2020">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2021">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2021">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2022">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2022">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2023">正規表現 Regex_canada_phin がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2023">The regular expression Regex_canada_phin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2024">2 つ以上のキーワードがKeyword_canada_phinまたはKeyword_canada_provinces検出されました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2024">At least two keywords from Keyword_canada_phin or Keyword_canada_provinces are found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada PHIN -->
<Entity id="722e12ac-c89a-4ec8-a1b7-fea3469f89db" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_phin" />
        <Any minMatches="2">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_phin" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_provinces" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-social-insurance-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2057">カナダの社会保険番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2057">Canada social insurance number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2058">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2058">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2059">9 桁の数字とオプションのハイフンまたはスペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2059">nine digits with optional hyphens or spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2060">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2060">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2061">書式設定:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2061">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2062">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2062">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2063">ハイフンまたはスペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2063">a hyphen or space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2064">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2064">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2065">ハイフンまたはスペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2065">a hyphen or space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2066">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2066">three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2067">書式設定されていない場合: 9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2067">Unformatted: nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2068">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2068">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2069">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2069">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2070">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2070">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2071">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2071">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2072">関数 Func_canadian_sin がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2072">The function Func_canadian_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2073">以下の 2 つ以上の条件に該当する:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2073">At least two of any combination of the following:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2074">Keyword_sin のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2074">A keyword from Keyword_sin is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2075">Keyword_sin_collaborative のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2075">A keyword from Keyword_sin_collaborative is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2076">関数 Func_eu_date が適切な日付形式の日付を検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2076">The function Func_eu_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2077">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2077">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2078">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2078">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2079">関数 Func_unformatted_canadian_sin がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2079">The function Func_unformatted_canadian_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2080">Keyword_sin のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2080">A keyword from Keyword_sin is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2081">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2081">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Social Insurance Number -->
<Entity id="a2f29c85-ecb8-4514-a610-364790c0773e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_canadian_sin" />
        <Any minMatches="2">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_sin" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_sin_collaborative" />
          <Match idRef="Func_eu_date" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_canadian_sin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_sin" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2103">誕生日</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2103">Birthdate</span></span>

## <a name="chile-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2106">チリの ID カード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2106">Chile identity card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2107">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2107">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2108">7 桁から 8 桁の数字と、チェック ディジットまたは文字の区切り文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2108">seven to eight digits plus delimiters a check digit or letter</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2109">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2109">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2110">7 ~ 8 桁の数字と区切り文字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2110">seven to eight digits plus delimiters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2111">1 桁から 2 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2111">one to two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2112">省略可能な期間</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2112">an optional period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2113">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2113">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2114">省略可能な期間</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2114">an optional period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2115">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2115">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2116">ダッシュ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2116">a dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2117">チェック ディジットである 1 桁の数字または文字 (大文字と小文字を区別しない)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2117">one digit or letter (not case-sensitive) which is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2118">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2118">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2119">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2119">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2120">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2120">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2121">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2121">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2122">この関数はFunc_chile_id_cardパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2122">The function Func_chile_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2123">検索されたKeyword_chile_id_card検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2123">A keyword from Keyword_chile_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2124">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2124">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2125">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2125">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2126">この関数はFunc_chile_id_cardパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2126">The function Func_chile_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2127">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2127">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Chile Identity Card Number -->
<Entity id="4e979794-49a0-407e-a0b9-2c536937b925" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_chile_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_chile_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_chile_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="china-resident-identity-card-prc-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2164">中国の住民識別カード (PRC) 番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2164">China resident identity card (PRC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2165">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2165">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2166">18 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2166">18 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2167">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2167">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2168">18 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2168">18 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2169">アドレス コードである 6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2169">six digits that are an address code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2170">YYYYMMDD という形式の 8 桁の数字 (生年月日)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2170">eight digits in the form YYYYMMDD, which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2171">注文コードである 3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2171">three digits that are an order code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2172">チェック ディジットである 1 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2172">one digit that is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2173">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2173">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2174">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2174">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2175">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2175">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2176">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2176">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2177">この関数はFunc_china_resident_idパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2177">The function Func_china_resident_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2178">検索されたKeyword_china_resident_id検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2178">A keyword from Keyword_china_resident_id is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2179">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2179">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2180">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2180">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2181">この関数はFunc_china_resident_idパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2181">The function Func_china_resident_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2182">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2182">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- China Resident Identity Card (PRC) Number -->
<Entity id="c92daa86-2d16-4871-901f-816b3f554fc1" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_china_resident_id"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_china_resident_id"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_china_resident_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2183">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2183">Keywords</span></span>

### <a name="keyword_china_resident_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2184">Keyword_china_resident_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2184">Keyword_china_resident_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2185">Resident Identity Card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2185">Resident Identity Card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2186">PRC</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2186">PRC</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2187">National Identification Card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2187">National Identification Card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2188">身份证</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2188">身份证</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2189">居民 身份证</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2189">居民 身份证</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2190">居民身份证</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2190">居民身份证</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2191">鉴定</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2191">鉴定</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2192">身分證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2192">身分證</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2193">居民 身份證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2193">居民 身份證</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2194">鑑定</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2194">鑑定</span></span> 

   
## <a name="credit-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2195">クレジット カード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2195">Credit card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2196">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2196">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2197">14 ~ 16 桁の数字。書式設定または書式設定解除が可能で (dddddddddddd)、Luhn テストに合格する必要があります。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2197">14 to 16 digits that can be formatted or unformatted (dddddddddddddddd) and that must pass the Luhn test.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2198">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2198">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2199">Visa、MasterCard、Discover Card、JCB、American Express、gift cards、およびdiner card など、世界中の主要ブランドのカードを検出する複雑で堅牢なパターン。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2199">Complex and robust pattern that detects cards from all major brands worldwide, including Visa, MasterCard, Discover Card, JCB, American Express, gift cards, and diner cards.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2200">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2200">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2201">あり (Luhn のチェックサム)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2201">Yes, the Luhn checksum</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2202">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2202">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2203">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2203">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2204">関数 Func_credit_card がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2204">The function Func_credit_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2205">次のいずれかの条件に該当する:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2205">One of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2206">Keyword_cc_verification のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2206">A keyword from Keyword_cc_verification is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2207">検索されたKeyword_cc_name見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2207">A keyword from Keyword_cc_name is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2208">関数 Func_expiration_date が適切な日付形式の日付を検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2208">The function Func_expiration_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2209">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2209">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2210">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたという信頼性が低い。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2210">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2211">関数 Func_credit_card がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2211">The function Func_credit_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2212">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2212">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Credit Card Number -->
<Entity id="50842eb7-edc8-4019-85dd-5a5c1f2bb085" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_credit_card" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_cc_verification" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_cc_name" />
          <Match idRef="Func_expiration_date" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_credit_card" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="croatia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2472">クロアチアの運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2472">Croatia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2473">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2473">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2474">スペースと区切り記号のない 8 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2474">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2475">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2475">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2476">8 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2476">eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2477">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2477">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2478">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2478">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2479">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2479">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2480">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2480">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2481">正規表現は、  `Regex_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2481">The regular expression  `Regex_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2482">キーワードが検出 `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2482">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
      <!-- Croatia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="005b3ef1-47dd-4e68-bb02-c6db484d00f2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="croatia-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2606">クロアチアの ID カード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2606">Croatia identity card number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2607">この機密情報の種類のエンティティは、EU の国民識別番号の機密情報の種類に含まれています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2607">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2608">スタンドアロンの機密情報の種類のエンティティとして使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2608">It's available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2609">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2609">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2610">9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2610">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2611">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2611">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2612">9 桁の連続する数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2612">nine consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2613">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2613">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2614">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2614">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2615">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2615">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2616">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2616">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2617">この関数はFunc_croatia_id_cardパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2617">The function Func_croatia_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2618">検索されたKeyword_croatia_id_card検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2618">A keyword from Keyword_croatia_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Croatia Identity Card Number-->
<Entity id="ff12f884-c20a-4189-b185-34c8e7258d47" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_croatia_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="croatia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2649">クロアチアのパスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2649">Croatia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2650">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2650">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2651">スペースと区切り記号のない 9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2651">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2652">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2652">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2653">9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2653">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2654">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2654">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2655">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2655">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2656">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2656">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2657">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2657">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2658">正規表現は、  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2658">The regular expression  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2659">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2659">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2660">正規表現が `Regex_eu_passport_date1` DD.MM.YYYY の形式で日付を検出するか、キーワードを `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 検出した</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2660">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2661">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2661">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2662">正規表現は、  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2662">The regular expression  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2663">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2663">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Croatia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="7d7a729d-32d8-4204-8d01-d5e6a6c25581" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2664">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2664">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2673">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2673">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2674">passportnumbers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2674">passportnumbers</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2675">パスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2675">passport numbers</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2676">Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2676">Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2677">broj putovovov</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2677">broj putovnice</span></span>

## <a name="croatia-personal-identification-oib-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2681">クロアチアの個人識別 (OIB) 番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2681">Croatia personal identification (OIB) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2682">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2682">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2683">11 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2683">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2684">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2684">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2685">11 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2685">11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2686">10 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2686">10 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2687">最終桁はチェック ディジット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2687">final digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2688">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2688">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2689">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2689">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2690">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2690">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2691">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2691">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2692">この関数はFunc_croatia_oib_numberパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2692">The function Func_croatia_oib_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2693">検索されたKeywords_croatia_eu_tax_file_number検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2693">A keyword from Keywords_croatia_eu_tax_file_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2694">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2694">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2695">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2695">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2696">この関数はFunc_croatia_oib_numberパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2696">The function Func_croatia_oib_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2697">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2697">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Croatia Personal Identification (OIB) Number -->
      <Entity id="31983b6d-db95-4eb2-a630-b44bd091968d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_oib_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_oib_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="croatia-social-security-number-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2728">クロアチアの社会保障番号または同等の識別情報</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2728">Croatia social security number or equivalent identification</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2729">この機密情報の種類のエンティティは、EU 社会保障番号または同等の ID の機密情報の種類でのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2729">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2730">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2730">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2731">スペースと区切り記号のない 11 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2731">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2732">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2732">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2733">11 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2733">11 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2734">10 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2734">10 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2735">1 桁のチェック ディジット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2735">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2736">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2736">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2737">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2737">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2738">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2738">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2739">DLP ポリシーは、抽出した約 300 文字が次の条件に該当することを検出した場合に、85% の確証を持ってそれがこの種類の機密情報であると特定します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2739">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2740">この関数は  `Func_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2740">The function  `Func_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2741">キーワードを  `Keywords_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2741">A keyword from  `Keywords_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2742">DLP ポリシーは、抽出した約 300 文字が次の条件に該当することを検出した場合に、75% の確証を持ってそれがこの種類の機密情報であると特定します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2742">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2743">この関数は  `Func_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2743">The function  `Func_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU SSN or Equivalent Number -->
<Entity id="d24e32a4-c0bb-4ba8-899d-6303b95742d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern> 
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>      
</Entity>
```

## <a name="cyprus-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2760">キプロスの運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2760">Cyprus drivers license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2761">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2761">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2762">スペースと区切り記号のない 12 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2762">12 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2763">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2763">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2764">12 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2764">12 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2765">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2765">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2766">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2766">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2767">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2767">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2768">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2768">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2769">正規表現は、  `Regex_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2769">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2770">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2770">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Cyprus Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="356fa104-f9ac-4aff-a0e4-2e6e65ea06c4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="cyprus-identity-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2895">キプロスの ID カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2895">Cyprus identity card</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2896">この機密情報の種類は、次の場合にのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2896">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2897">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2897">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2898">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2898">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2899">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2899">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2900">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2900">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2901">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2901">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2902">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2902">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2903">スペースと区切り記号のない 10 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2903">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2904">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2904">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2905">10 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2905">10 digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2906">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2906">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2907">該当なし</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2907">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2908">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2908">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2909">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2909">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2910">正規表現は、  `Regex_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2910">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2911">キーワードを  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` 検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2911">A keyword from  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml 
      <!-- Cyprus Identity Card -->
      <Entity id="3ba8afe5-7a6c-4929-8247-0001b6878438" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2912">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2912">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2913">Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2913">Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2914">id card number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2914">id card number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2915">ID カード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2915">identity card number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2916">kim kim karti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2916">kimlik karti</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2917">national identification number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2917">national identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2918">個人用 ID 番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2918">personal id number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2919">ταυτοτητασ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2919">ταυτοτητασ</span></span>


## <a name="cyprus-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2920">キプロスのパスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2920">Cyprus passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2921">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2921">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2922">1 文字の後に 6 ~ 8 桁の数字 (スペースまたは区切り記号なし)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2922">one letter followed by 6-8 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2923">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2923">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2924">1 文字の後に 6 ~ 8 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2924">one letter followed by six to eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2925">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2925">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2926">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2926">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2927">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2927">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2928">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2928">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2929">正規表現は、  `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2929">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2930">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2930">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2931">正規表現が `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_date` DD/MM/YYYY の形式で日付を検出するか、キーワードが `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_date` 見つかった</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2931">The regular expression `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD/MM/YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2932">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2932">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2933">正規表現は、  `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2933">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2934">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2934">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>  
    
```xml
      <!-- Cyprus Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="9193e2e8-7f8c-43c1-a274-ac40d651936f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
