## <a name="cyprus-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2963">キプロスの税金の識別番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2963">Cyprus tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2964">この機密情報の種類は、次の場合にのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2964">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2965">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2965">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2966">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2966">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2967">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2967">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2968">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2968">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2969">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2969">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2970">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2970">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2971">指定されたパターンの 8 桁の数字と 1 文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2971">eight digits and one letter in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2972">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2972">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2973">8 桁の数字と 1 文字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2973">eight digits and one letter:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2974">"0" または "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2974">a "0" or "9"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2975">7 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2975">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2976">1 文字 (大文字と小文字を区別しない)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2976">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2977">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2977">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2978">該当なし</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2978">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2979">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2979">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2980">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2980">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2981">この関数は  `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` 、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2981">The function  `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2982">キーワードを  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` 検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2982">A keyword from  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2983">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2983">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2984">この関数は  `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` 、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2984">The function  `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Cyprus Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="40e64bd9-55f3-4a09-9bd6-1db18dced9dd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2986">Keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2986">Keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-2991">tax no#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-2991">tax no#</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3006">vergi kimino kodu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3006">vergi kimlik kodu</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3007">vergi kim numaras Numaras の数</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3007">vergi kimlik numarası</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3008">αριθμός φορολογικού μητρώου</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3008">αριθμός φορολογικού μητρώου</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3011">φορολογικού κωδικού</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3011">φορολογικού κωδικού</span></span>


## <a name="czech-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3012">チェコ語の運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3012">Czech driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3013">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3013">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3014">2 桁の文字の後に 6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3014">two letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3015">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3015">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3016">8 桁の文字と数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3016">eight letters and digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3017">文字 'E' (大文字と小文字を区別しない)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3017">letter 'E' (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3018">レター</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3018">a letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3019">スペース (省略可能)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3019">a space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3020">6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3020">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3021">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3021">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3022">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3022">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3023">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3023">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3024">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3024">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3025">正規表現は、  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3025">The regular expression  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3026">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3026">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
      <Entity id="86b40d3b-d8ea-4c36-aab0-ef9416a6769c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3027">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3027">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3028">Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3028">Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number</span></span>

## <a name="czech-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3152">チェコのパスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3152">Czech passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3153">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3153">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3154">スペースまたは区切り記号を含めずに 8 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3154">eight digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3155">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3155">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3156">スペースまたは区切り記号を含めずに 8 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3156">eight digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3157">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3157">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3158">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3158">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3159">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3159">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3160">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3160">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3161">正規表現は、  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3161">The regular expression  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3162">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3162">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3163">正規表現が `Regex_eu_passport_date1` DD.MM.YYYY の形式で日付を検出するか、キーワードを `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 検出した</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3163">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3164">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3164">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3165">正規表現は、  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3165">The regular expression  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3166">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3166">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Czech Republic Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="7bcd8ce8-5e92-4bbe-bc92-fa669f0369fa" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="czech-personal-identity-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3188">チェコの個人識別番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3188">Czech personal identity number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3189">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3189">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3190">9 桁の数字 (オプションのスラッシュ (古い形式) 10 桁の数字とオプションのスラッシュ (新しい形式)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3190">nine digits with optional forward slash (old format) 10 digits with optional forward slash (new format)</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3191">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3191">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3192">9 桁の数字 (古い形式):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3192">nine digits (old format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3193">生年月日を表す 6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3193">six digits that represent date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3194">オプションのスラッシュ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3194">an optional forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3195">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3195">three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3196">10 桁の数字 (新しい形式):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3196">10 digits (new format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3197">生年月日を表す 6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3197">six digits that represent date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3198">オプションのスラッシュ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3198">an optional forward slash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3199">最後の数字がチェック ディジットである 4 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3199">four digits where last digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3200">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3200">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3201">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3201">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3202">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3202">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3203">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3203">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3204">この関数はFunc_czech_id_cardパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3204">The function Func_czech_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3205">検索されたKeyword_czech_id_card検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3205">A keyword from Keyword_czech_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3206">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3206">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3207">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3207">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3208">この関数はFunc_czech_id_card_new_formatパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3208">The function Func_czech_id_card_new_format finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3209">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3209">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Czech Personal Identity Number -->
      <!-- Czech Personal Identity Number -->
      <Entity id="60c0725a-4eb6-455b-9dda-05d8a7396497" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_czech_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_czech_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Version minEngineVersion="15.20.3000.000">
          <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
            <IdMatch idRef="Func_czech_id_card_new_format" />
          </Pattern>
        </Version>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="czech-social-security-number-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3256">チェコの社会保障番号または同等の識別情報</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3256">Czech social security number or equivalent identification</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3257">この機密情報の種類のエンティティは、EU 社会保障番号または同等の ID の機密情報の種類でのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3257">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3258">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3258">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3259">指定したパターンの 10 桁の数字と円記号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3259">10 digits and a backslash in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3260">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3260">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3261">10 桁の数字とバックスラッシュ:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3261">10 digits and a backslash:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3262">生年月日 (YYMMDD) に対応する 6 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3262">six digits that correspond to the birth date (YYMMDD):</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3263">円記号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3263">a backslash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3264">同じ日付に生まれた人物を分け合うシリアル番号に対応する 3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3264">three digits that correspond to a serial number that separates persons born on the same date</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3265">1 桁のチェック ディジット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3265">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3266">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3266">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3267">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3267">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3268">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3268">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3269">DLP ポリシーは、抽出した約 300 文字が次の条件に該当することを検出した場合に、85% の確証を持ってそれがこの種類の機密情報であると特定します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3269">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3270">この関数は  `Func_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3270">The function  `Func_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3271">キーワードを  `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3271">A keyword from  `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3272">DLP ポリシーは、抽出した約 300 文字が次の条件に該当することを検出した場合に、75% の確証を持ってそれがこの種類の機密情報であると特定します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3272">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3273">この関数は  `Func_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3273">The function  `Func_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 

```xml
 <!-- EU SSN or Equivalent Number -->
<Entity id="d24e32a4-c0bb-4ba8-899d-6303b95742d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern> 
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>      
</Entity>
```

## <a name="denmark-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3289">デンマークの運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3289">Denmark driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3290">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3290">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3291">スペースと区切り記号のない 8 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3291">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3292">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3292">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3293">8 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3293">eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3294">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3294">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3295">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3295">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3296">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3296">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3297">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3297">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3298">正規表現は、  `Regex_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3298">The regular expression  `Regex_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3299">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3299">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Denmark Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="98a95812-6203-451a-a220-d39870ebef0e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="denmark-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3423">デンマークのパスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3423">Denmark passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3424">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3424">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3425">スペースと区切り記号のない 9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3425">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3426">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3426">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3427">9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3427">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3428">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3428">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3429">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3429">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3430">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3430">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3431">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3431">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3432">正規表現は、  `Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3432">The regular expression  `Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3433">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3433">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3434">DD MM YY またはキーワードの形式で日付が検出 `Regex_eu_passport_date2` された正規表現 `Keywords_eu_passport_date` が見つかった</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3434">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date2` finds date in the format DD MM YY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3435">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3435">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3436">正規表現は、  `Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3436">The regular expression  `Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3437">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3437">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Denmark Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="25e8c47e-e6fe-4884-a211-74898f8c0196" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date2" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

## <a name="denmark-personal-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3457">デンマークの個人識別番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3457">Denmark personal identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3458">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3458">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3459">ハイフンを 1 つ含む 10 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3459">10 digits containing a hyphen</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3460">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3460">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3461">10 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3461">10 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3462">DDMMYY という形式の 6 桁の数字 (生年月日)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3462">six digits in the format DDMMYY, which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3463">ハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3463">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3464">最後の桁がチェック ディジットである 4 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3464">four digits where the final digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3465">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3465">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3466">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3466">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3467">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3467">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3468">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3468">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3469">パターンに一Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_numberコンテンツを検索する正規表現。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3469">The regular expression Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3470">検索されたKeyword_denmark_id検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3470">A keyword from Keyword_denmark_id is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3471">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3471">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3472">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたという信頼性が低い。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3472">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3473">パターンに一Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_numberコンテンツを検索する正規表現。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3473">The regular expression Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3474">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3474">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Denmark Personal Identification Number -->
      <!-- Denmark Personal Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="6c4f2fef-56e1-4c00-8093-88d7a01cf460" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_denmark_id" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3485">医療保険番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3485">health insurance number</span></span>

## <a name="denmark-social-security-number-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3546">デンマークの社会保障番号または同等の識別情報</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3546">Denmark social security number or equivalent identification</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3547">この機密情報の種類のエンティティは、EU 社会保障番号または同等の ID の機密情報の種類のみを使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3547">This sensitive information type entity is only available the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3548">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3548">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3549">指定したパターンの 10 桁の数字とハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3549">10 digits and a hyphen in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3550">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3550">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3551">10 桁の数字とハイフン:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3551">10 digits and a hyphen:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3552">生年月日に対応する 6 桁の数字 (DDMMYY)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3552">six digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMYY)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3553">ハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3553">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3554">シーケンス番号に対応する 4 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3554">four digits that correspond to a sequence number</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3555">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3555">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3556">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3556">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3557">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3557">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3558">DLP ポリシーは、抽出した約 300 文字が次の条件に該当することを検出した場合に、85% の確証を持ってそれがこの種類の機密情報であると特定します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3558">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3559">この関数は  `Func_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3559">The function  `Func_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3560">キーワードを  `Keywords_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3560">A keyword from  `Keywords_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3561">DLP ポリシーは、抽出した約 300 文字が次の条件に該当することを検出した場合に、75% の確証を持ってそれがこの種類の機密情報であると特定します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3561">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3562">この関数は  `Func_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3562">The function  `Func_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU SSN or Equivalent Number -->
<Entity id="d24e32a4-c0bb-4ba8-899d-6303b95742d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern> 
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>      
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3563">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3563">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3564">Keywords_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3564">Keywords_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3567">social security number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3567">social security number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3568">nationalnumber#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3568">nationalnumber#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3569">ssn#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3569">ssn#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3570">ssn</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3570">ssn</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3571">national number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3571">national number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3573">personalidnumber#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3573">personalidnumber#</span></span>

## <a name="drug-enforcement-agency-dea-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3576">ドラッグ執行機関 (DEA) 番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3576">Drug Enforcement Agency (DEA) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3577">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3577">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3578">2 桁の文字の後に 7 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3578">two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3579">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3579">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3580">パターンには、以下のすべてが含まれる必要があります。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3580">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3581">考えられる文字セットの 1 文字 (大文字と小文字は区別されません): abcdefghjklmnprstux(登録コード)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3581">one letter (not case-sensitive) from this set of possible letters: abcdefghjklmnprstux, which is a registrant code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3582">1 文字 (大文字と小文字は区別されません)。これは、登録者の名の最初の文字または数字 '9' です。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3582">one letter (not case-sensitive), which is the first letter of the registrant's last name or digit '9'</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3583">7 桁の数字、最後の数字はチェック ディジット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3583">seven digits, the last of which is the check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3584">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3584">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3585">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3585">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3586">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3586">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3587">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3587">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3588">関数 Func_dea_number がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3588">The function Func_dea_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3589">キーワード `Keyword_dea_number` の検索</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3589">A keyword from `Keyword_dea_number` is found</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3590">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3590">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3591">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3591">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3592">関数 Func_dea_number がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3592">The function Func_dea_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3593">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3593">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- DEA Number -->
    <Entity id="9a5445ad-406e-43eb-8bd7-cac17ab6d0e4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_dea_number" />
      </Pattern>
      <Version minEngineVersion="15.20.1207.000" maxEngineVersion="15.20.3134.000">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_dea_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Version>
      <Version minEngineVersion="15.20.3135.000">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_dea_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_dea_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Version>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3594">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3594">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_dea_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3595">Keyword_dea_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3595">Keyword_dea_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3596">dea</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3596">dea</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3597">dea#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3597">dea#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3598">ドラッグの実施の管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3598">drug enforcement administration</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3599">ドラッグ執行機関</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3599">drug enforcement agency</span></span>


## <a name="estonia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3600">エストニアの運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3600">Estonia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3601">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3601">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3602">2 桁の文字の後に 6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3602">two letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3603">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3603">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3604">2 桁の文字と 6 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3604">two letters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3605">文字 "ET" (大文字と小文字を区別しない)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3605">the letters "ET" (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3606">6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3606">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3607">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3607">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3608">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3608">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3609">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3609">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3610">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3610">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3611">正規表現は、  `Regex_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3611">The regular expression  `Regex_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3612">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3612">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Estonia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="51da8171-da70-4cc1-9d65-055a59ca4f83" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="estonia-personal-identification-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3738">エストニアの個人識別コード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3738">Estonia Personal Identification Code</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3739">この機密情報の種類は、次の場合にのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3739">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3740">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3740">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3741">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3741">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3742">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3742">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3743">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3743">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3744">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3744">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3745">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3745">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3746">スペースと区切り記号のない 11 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3746">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3747">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3747">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3748">11 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3748">11 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3749">性と生年月日に対応する 1 桁の数字 (奇数の男性、偶数の女性、1 ~ 2: 19th century、3 ~ 4: 20th century、5 ~ 6: 21st century)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3749">one digit that corresponds to sex and century of birth (odd number male, even number female; 1-2: 19th century; 3-4: 20th century; 5-6: 21st century)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3750">生年月日 (YYMMDD) に対応する 6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3750">six digits that correspond to date of birth (YYMMDD)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3751">同じ日付に生まれた人を区切るシリアル番号に対応する 3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3751">three digits that correspond to a serial number separating persons born on the same date</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3752">1 桁のチェック ディジット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3752">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3753">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3753">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3754">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3754">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3755">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3755">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3756">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3756">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3757">この関数は  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` 、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3757">The function  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3758">キーワードを  `Keywords_estonia_eu_national_id_card` 検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3758">A keyword from  `Keywords_estonia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3759">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3759">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3760">この関数は  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` 、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3760">The function  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Estonia Personal Identification Code -->
      <Entity id="bfb26de6-dad5-4d48-ab72-4789cdd0654c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="estonia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3793">エストニアのパスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3793">Estonia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3794">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3794">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3795">1 文字の後に 7 桁の数字 (スペースまたは区切り記号なし)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3795">one letter followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3796">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3796">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3797">1 文字の後に 7 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3797">one letter followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3798">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3798">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3799">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3799">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3800">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3800">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3801">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3801">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3802">正規表現は、  `Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3802">The regular expression  `Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3803">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3803">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3804">正規表現が `Regex_eu_passport_date1` DD.MM.YYYY の形式で日付を検出するか、キーワードを `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 検出した</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3804">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3805">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3805">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3806">正規表現は、  `Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3806">The regular expression  `Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3807">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3807">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Estonia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="61f7073a-509e-425b-a754-bc01bb5d5b8c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="eu-debit-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3825">EU のデビット カード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3825">EU debit card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3826">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3826">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3827">16 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3827">16 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3828">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3828">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3829">複雑で堅牢なパターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3829">Complex and robust pattern</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3830">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3830">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3831">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3831">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3832">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3832">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3833">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3833">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3834">関数 Func_eu_debit_card がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3834">The function Func_eu_debit_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3835">次の条件のうち 1 つ以上に該当する:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3835">At least one of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3836">Keyword_eu_debit_card のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3836">A keyword from Keyword_eu_debit_card is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3837">Keyword_card_terms_dict のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3837">A keyword from Keyword_card_terms_dict is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3838">Keyword_card_security_terms_dict のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3838">A keyword from Keyword_card_security_terms_dict is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3839">Keyword_card_expiration_terms_dict のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3839">A keyword from Keyword_card_expiration_terms_dict is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3840">関数 Func_expiration_date が適切な日付形式の日付を検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3840">The function Func_expiration_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-3841">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-3841">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- EU Debit Card Number -->
    <Entity id="0e9b3178-9678-47dd-a509-37222ca96b42" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_eu_debit_card" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_eu_debit_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_card_terms_dict" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_card_security_terms_dict" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_card_expiration_terms_dict" />
          <Match idRef="Func_expiration_date" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="finland-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4288">フィンランドの運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4288">Finland driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4289">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4289">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4290">ハイフンを 1 つ含む 10 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4290">10 digits containing a hyphen</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4291">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4291">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4292">ハイフンを含む 10 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4292">10 digits containing a hyphen:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4293">6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4293">six digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4294">ハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4294">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4295">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4295">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4296">1 桁の数字または文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4296">a digit or letter</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4297">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4297">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4298">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4298">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4299">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4299">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4300">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4300">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4301">正規表現は、  `Regex_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4301">The regular expression  `Regex_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4302">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4302">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Finland Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="bb3b27a3-79bd-4ac4-81a7-f9fca3c7d1a7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_finland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_finland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4303">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4303">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4304">Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4304">Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4305">driverlic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4305">driverlic</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4306">driverlics</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4306">driverlics</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4307">driverlicense</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4307">driverlicense</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4308">driverlicenses</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4308">driverlicenses</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4309">driverlicence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4309">driverlicence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4310">driverlicences</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4310">driverlicences</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4311">driver lic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4311">driver lic</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4312">driver lics</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4312">driver lics</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4313">driver license</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4313">driver license</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4446">10 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4446">10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4447">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4447">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4448">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4448">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4449">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4449">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4450">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4450">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4451">正規表現はRegex_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Numberパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4451">The regex Regex_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4452">検索されたKeyword_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4452">A keyword from Keyword_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Finland European Health Insurance Number -->
      <Entity id="60f75aed-81bf-4625-89b0-0846b9248ee7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="finland-national-id"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4470">フィンランドの国民 ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4470">Finland national ID</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4471">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4471">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4472">6 桁の数字と、100 年に 3 桁の数字とチェック ディジットを示す文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4472">six digits plus a character indicating a century plus three digits plus a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4473">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4473">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4474">パターンには、以下のすべてが含まれる必要があります。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4474">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4475">DDMMYY という形式の 6 桁の数字 (生年月日)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4475">six digits in the format DDMMYY, which are a date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4476">century マーカー ('-'、'+'、または 'a')</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4476">century marker (either '-', '+' or 'a')</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4477">3 桁の個人識別番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4477">three-digit personal identification number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4478">チェック ディジットである数字または文字 (大文字と小文字を区別しない)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4478">a digit or letter (case insensitive) which is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4479">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4479">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4480">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4480">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4481">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4481">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4482">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4482">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4483">関数はFunc_finnish_national_idパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4483">the function Func_finnish_national_id finds content that matches the pattern</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4484">検索されたKeyword_finnish_national_id検出された</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4484">a keyword from Keyword_finnish_national_id is found</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4485">チェックサムが渡される</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4485">the checksum passes</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4486">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4486">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4487">関数はFunc_finnish_national_idパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4487">the function Func_finnish_national_id finds content that matches the pattern</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4488">チェックサムが渡される</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4488">the checksum passes</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Finnish National ID-->
      <Entity id="338FD995-4CB5-4F87-AD35-79BD1DD926C1" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_finnish_national_id" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_finnish_national_id" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_finnish_national_id" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="finland-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4537">フィンランドのパスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4537">Finland passport number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4538">この機密情報の種類のエンティティは、EU パスポート番号の機密情報の種類で利用できます。スタンドアロンの機密情報の種類のエンティティとして使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4538">This sensitive information type entity is available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4539">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4539">Format</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4540">9 桁の文字と数字の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4540">combination of nine letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4541">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4541">Pattern</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4542">9 桁の文字と数字の組み合わせ:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4542">combination of nine letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4543">2 文字 (大文字と小文字を区別しない)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4543">two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4544">7 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4544">seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4545">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4545">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4546">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4546">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4547">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4547">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4548">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4548">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4549">正規表現は、 `Regex_finland_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4549">The regular expression `Regex_finland_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4550">キーワードが検出 `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keyword_finland_passport_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4550">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keyword_finland_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4551">正規表現が `Regex_eu_passport_date1` DD.MM.YYYY の形式で日付を検出するか、キーワードを `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 検出した</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4551">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4552">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4552">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4553">正規表現は、 `Regex_finland_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4553">The regular expression `Regex_finland_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4554">キーワードが検出 `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keyword_finland_passport_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4554">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keyword_finland_passport_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Finland Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="d1685ac3-1d3a-40f8-8198-32ef5669c7a5" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_finland_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_finland_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_finland_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_finland_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="france-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4578">フランスの運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4578">France driver's license number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4579">この機密情報の種類のエンティティは、EU の運転免許証番号の機密情報の種類で利用できます。スタンドアロンの機密情報の種類のエンティティとして使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4579">This sensitive information type entity is available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4580">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4580">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4581">12 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4581">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4582">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4582">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4583">フランスの電話番号などの同様のパターンと区別するための検証付きの 12 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4583">12 digits with validation to discount similar patterns such as French telephone numbers</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4584">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4584">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4585">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4585">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4586">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4586">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4587">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4587">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4588">関数はFunc_french_drivers_licenseパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4588">the function Func_french_drivers_license finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-4589">検索されたKeyword_french_drivers_license検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-4589">a keyword from Keyword_french_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- France Driver's License Number -->
    <Entity id="18e55a36-a01b-4b0f-943d-dc10282a1824" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_french_drivers_license" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_french_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```
