## <a name="lithuania-personal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7336">リトアニアの個人コード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7336">Lithuania personal code</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7337">この機密情報の種類は、次の場合にのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7337">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7338">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7338">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7339">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7339">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7340">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7340">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7341">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7341">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7342">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7342">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7343">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7343">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7344">スペースと区切り記号のない 11 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7344">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7345">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7345">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7346">スペースと区切り記号のない 11 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7346">11 digits without spaces and delimiters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7347">性別と出生後の年齢に対応する 1 桁の数字 (1 ~ 6)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7347">one digit (1-6) that corresponds to the person's gender and century of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7348">生年月日に対応する 6 桁の数字 (YYMMDD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7348">six digits that correspond to birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7349">生年月日のシリアル番号に対応する 3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7349">three digits that correspond to the serial number of the date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7350">1 桁のチェック ディジット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7350">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7351">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7351">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7352">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7352">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7353">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7353">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7354">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7354">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7355">この関数は  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` 、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7355">The function  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7356">キーワードを  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` 検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7356">A keyword from  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7357">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7357">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7358">この関数は  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` 、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7358">The function  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Lithuania Personal Code -->
      <Entity id="cd6d3786-8ec3-4524-a2cf-1e0095379171" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="lithuania-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7393">リトアニアのパスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7393">Lithuania passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7394">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7394">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7395">スペースまたは区切り文字を含めない 8 桁の数字または文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7395">eight digits or letters with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7396">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7396">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7397">8 桁の数字または文字 (大文字と小文字を区別しない)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7397">eight digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7398">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7398">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7399">該当なし</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7399">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7400">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7400">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7401">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7401">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7402">正規表現は、  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7402">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7403">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7403">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7404">正規表現で DD MM YYYY という形式の日付が検出された場合、またはキーワード `Regex_eu_passport_date3` が `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 検出された場合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7404">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date3` finds date in the format DD MM YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7405">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7405">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7406">正規表現は、  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7406">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7407">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7407">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Lithuania Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="1b79900f-047b-4c3f-846f-7d73b5534bce" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date3" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7427">ジェムバーガーの運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7427">Luxemburg driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7428">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7428">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7429">スペースと区切り記号のない 6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7429">six digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7430">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7430">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7431">6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7431">six digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7432">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7432">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7433">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7433">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7434">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7434">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7435">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7435">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7436">正規表現は、  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7436">The regular expression  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7437">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7437">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="89daf717-1544-4860-9a2e-fc9166dd8852" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-national-identification-number-natural-persons"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7561">ウレンザフの国民識別番号 (自然人)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7561">Luxemburg national identification number (natural persons)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7562">この機密情報の種類は、次の場合にのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7562">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7563">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7563">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7564">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7564">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7565">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7565">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7566">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7566">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7567">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7567">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7568">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7568">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7569">13 桁の数字 (スペースまたは区切り記号なし)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7569">13 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7570">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7570">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7571">13 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7571">13 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7572">11 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7572">11 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7573">2 桁のチェック ディジット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7573">two check digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7574">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7574">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7575">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7575">yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7576">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7576">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7577">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7577">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7578">この関数は  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` 、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7578">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7579">キーワードを  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card` 検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7579">A keyword from  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7580">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7580">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7581">この関数は  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` 、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7581">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 


```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg National Identification Number (Natural persons) -->
      <Entity id="aaf661ed-29ec-426d-8bf9-880cad298ebb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7604">ジェムザフのパスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7604">Luxemburg passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7605">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7605">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7606">スペースまたは区切り文字を含めない 8 桁の数字または文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7606">eight digits or letters with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7607">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7607">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7608">8 桁の数字または文字 (大文字と小文字を区別しない)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7608">eight digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7609">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7609">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7610">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7610">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7611">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7611">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7612">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7612">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7613">正規表現は、  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7613">The regular expression  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7614">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7614">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7615">正規表現で DD MM YYYY という形式の日付が検出された場合、またはキーワード `Regex_eu_passport_date3` が `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 検出された場合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7615">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date3` finds date in the format DD MM YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7616">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7616">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7617">正規表現は、  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7617">The regular expression  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7618">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7618">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="81d5c027-bed9-4421-91a0-3b2e55b3eb85" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date3" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-national-identification-number-non-natural-persons"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7650">ウレンザフの国民識別番号 (非自然人)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7650">Luxemburg national identification number (non-natural persons)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7651">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7651">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7652">11 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7652">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7653">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7653">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7654">11 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7654">11 digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7655">2 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7655">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7656">省略可能なスペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7656">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7657">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7657">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7658">省略可能なスペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7658">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7659">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7659">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7660">省略可能なスペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7660">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7661">2 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7661">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7662">1 桁のチェック ディジット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7662">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7663">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7663">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7664">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7664">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7665">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7665">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7666">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7666">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7667">この関数は  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` 、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7667">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7668">キーワードを  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` 検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7668">A keyword from  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7669">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7669">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7670">この関数は  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` 、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7670">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg National Identification Number (Non-natural persons) -->
      <Entity id="84bffa3a-d805-4788-a613-b1e4df3804cf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="malaysia-identification-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7710">マレーシアの識別カード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7710">Malaysia identification card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7711">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7711">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7712">省略可能なハイフンを含む 12 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7712">12 digits containing optional hyphens</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7713">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7713">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7714">12 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7714">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7715">YYMMDD 形式の 6 桁の数字 (生年月日)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7715">six digits in the format YYMMDD, which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7716">ダッシュ (省略可能)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7716">a dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7717">2 文字の出生時コード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7717">two-letter place-of-birth code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7718">ダッシュ (省略可能)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7718">a dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7719">3 桁のランダムな数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7719">three random digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7720">1 桁の性別コード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7720">one-digit gender code</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7721">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7721">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7722">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7722">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7723">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7723">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7724">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7724">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7725">パターンに一Regex_malaysia_id_card_numberコンテンツを検索する正規表現。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7725">The regular expression Regex_malaysia_id_card_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7726">検索されたKeyword_malaysia_id_card_number検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7726">A keyword from Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Malaysia ID Card Number -->
</Entity>
      <Entity id="7f0e921c-9677-435b-aba2-bb8f1013c749" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
            <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malaysia_id_card_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7727">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7727">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_malaysia_id_card_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7728">Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7728">Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7729">デジタル アプリケーション カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7729">digital application card</span></span>

## <a name="malta-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7753">マルタの運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7753">Malta driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7754">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7754">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7755">指定したパターンでの 2 文字と 6 桁の数字の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7755">Combination of two characters and six digits in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7756">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7756">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7757">2 文字と 6 桁の数字の組み合わせ:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7757">combination of two characters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7758">2 文字 (数字または文字、大文字と小文字を区別しない)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7758">two characters (digits or letters, not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7759">スペース (省略可能)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7759">a space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7760">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7760">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7761">スペース (省略可能)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7761">a space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7762">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7762">three digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7763">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7763">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7764">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7764">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7765">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7765">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7766">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7766">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7767">正規表現は、  `Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7767">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7768">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7768">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="a3bdaa4a-8371-4735-8fa5-56ee0fb4afc4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="malta-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7892">マルタの ID カード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7892">Malta identity card number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7893">この機密情報の種類は、次の場合にのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7893">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7894">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7894">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7895">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7895">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7896">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7896">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7897">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7897">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7898">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7898">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7899">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7899">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7900">7 桁の数字の後に 1 文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7900">seven digits followed by one letter</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7901">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7901">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7902">7 桁の数字の後に 1 文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7902">seven digits followed by one letter:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7903">7 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7903">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7904">"M, G, A, P, L, H, B, Z" の 1 文字 (大文字と小文字を区別しない)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7904">one letter in "M, G, A, P, L, H, B, Z" (case insensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7905">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7905">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7906">該当なし</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7906">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7907">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7907">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7908">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7908">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7909">正規表現は、  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7909">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7910">キーワードを  `Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card` 検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7910">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7911">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたという信頼性が低い。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7911">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7912">正規表現は、  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7912">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Identity Card Number -->
      <Entity id="854b36b3-a388-4ac8-a4ec-677c2b5e4356" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7921">numru ta 'identifikazzjoni un un"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7921">numru ta 'identifikazzjoni uniku</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7922">numru ta' identità un un</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7922">numru ta' identità uniku</span></span>

## <a name="malta-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7929">マルタのパスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7929">Malta passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7930">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7930">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7931">スペースまたは区切り記号のない 7 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7931">seven digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7932">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7932">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7933">7 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7933">seven digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7934">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7934">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7935">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7935">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7936">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7936">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7937">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7937">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7938">正規表現は、  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7938">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7939">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7939">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7940">キーワード `Keywords_eu_passport_date` の検索</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7940">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7941">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7941">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7942">正規表現は、  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7942">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7943">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7943">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="b2b21198-48f9-4d13-b2a5-03969bff0fb8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7961">発行日</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7961">date of issue</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7962">有効期限日</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7962">date of expiry</span></span>


## <a name="malta-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7963">マルタの税金の識別番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7963">Malta tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7964">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7964">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7965">マルタの国民の場合:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7965">For Maltese nationals:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7966">指定されたパターンの 7 桁の数字と 1 文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7966">seven digits and one letter in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7967">マルタ以外の国民およびマルタのエンティティ:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7967">Non-Maltese nationals and Maltese entities:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7968">9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7968">nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7969">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7969">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7970">マルタの国民: 7 桁の数字と 1 文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7970">Maltese nationals: seven digits and one letter</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7971">7 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7971">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7972">1 文字 (大文字と小文字を区別しない)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7972">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7973">マルタ以外の国民およびマルタのエンティティ: 9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7973">Non-Maltese nationals and Maltese entities: nine digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7974">9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7974">nine digits</span></span> 
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7975">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7975">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7976">該当なし</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7976">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7977">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7977">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7978">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7978">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7979">regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number`  または `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7979">The regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number`  or `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7980">キーワードを  `Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number` 検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7980">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7981">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたという信頼性が低い。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7981">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7982">regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number` または `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7982">The regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number` or `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Tax ID Number -->
      <Entity id="ec830c63-65f4-45d0-9d8c-910dc8334b20" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7983">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7983">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7988">kodiċi numerali personali</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7988">kodiċi numerali personali</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7992">numru ta' identità un un</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7992">numru ta' identità uniku</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7993">numru tas-servizz taċ-ċittadin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7993">numru tas-servizz taċ-ċittadin</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-7998">税識別番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-7998">tax identification number</span></span>

## <a name="netherlands-citizens-service-bsn-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8015">オランダの市民サービス (BSN) 番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8015">Netherlands citizen's service (BSN) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8016">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8016">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8017">省略可能なスペースを含む 8 桁または 9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8017">eight or nine digits containing optional spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8018">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8018">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8019">8 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8019">eight-nine digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8020">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8020">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8021">スペース (省略可能)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8021">a space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8022">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8022">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8023">スペース (省略可能)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8023">a space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8024">2 桁の 3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8024">two-three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8025">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8025">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8026">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8026">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8027">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8027">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8028">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8028">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8029">この関数はFunc_netherlands_bsnパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8029">The function Func_netherlands_bsn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8030">検索されたKeyword_netherlands_bsn検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8030">A keyword from Keyword_netherlands_bsn is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8031">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8031">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Citizen's Service (BSN) Number -->
      <Entity id="c5f54253-ef7e-44f6-a578-440ed67e946d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_bsn" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8032">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8032">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_netherlands_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8033">Keywords_netherlands_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8033">Keywords_netherlands_eu_national_id_card</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8034">bsn#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8034">bsn#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8035">bsn</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8035">bsn</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8036">servicenummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8036">burgerservicenummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8037">citizen service number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8037">citizen service number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8038">ユーザー番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8038">person number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8039">個人番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8039">personal number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8040">個人の数値コード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8040">personal numeric code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8041">人物関連の番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8041">person-related number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8042">persoonlijk nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8042">persoonlijk nummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8043">persoonlijke numjkke コード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8043">persoonlijke numerieke code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8044">persoonsge最も近い</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8044">persoonsgebonden</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8045">persoonsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8045">persoonsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8046">sociaal-fiscaal nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8046">sociaal-fiscaal nummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8047">social-fiscal number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8047">social-fiscal number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8048">sofi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8048">sofi</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8049">sofinummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8049">sofinummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8050">uniek identificatienummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8050">uniek identificatienummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8051">uniek identiteitsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8051">uniek identiteitsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8052">一意の ID 番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8052">unique identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8053">一意の ID 番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8053">unique identity number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8054">uniqueidentityno#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8054">uniqueidentityno#</span></span>

## <a name="netherlands-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8055">オランダの運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8055">Netherlands driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8056">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8056">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8057">スペースと区切り記号のない 10 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8057">ten digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8058">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8058">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8059">10 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8059">ten digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8060">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8060">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8061">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8061">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8062">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8062">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8063">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8063">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8064">正規表現は、  `Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8064">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8065">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8065">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="6247fbea-ab80-4be5-8233-308b7c031401" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
```

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8198">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8198">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8199">該当なし</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8199">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8200">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8200">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8201">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8201">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8202">正規表現は、  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8202">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8203">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8203">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8204">正規表現が `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_date` DD MMM/MMM YYYY の形式で日付を検索する (例 - 26 THE/MAR 2012)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8204">The regular expression `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format  DD MMM/MMM YYYY (Example - 26 MAA/MAR 2012)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8205">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8205">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8206">正規表現は、  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8206">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8207">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8207">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="61786727-bafd-45f6-94d9-888d815e228e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_date" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8225">オランダの税金の識別番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8225">Netherlands tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8226">この機密情報の種類は、次の場合にのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8226">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8227">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8227">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8228">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8228">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8229">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8229">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8230">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8230">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8231">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8231">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8232">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8232">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8233">スペースまたは区切り記号のない 9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8233">nine digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8234">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8234">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8235">9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8235">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8236">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8236">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8237">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8237">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8238">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8238">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8239">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8239">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8240">この関数は  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` 、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8240">The function  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8241">キーワードを  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` 検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8241">A keyword from  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8242">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたという信頼性が低い。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8242">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8243">この関数は  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` 、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8243">The function  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="01f42a64-eba7-4892-a67b-398237e4ade2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8281">オランダの付加価値税番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8281">Netherlands value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8282">この機密情報の種類は、次の場合にのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8282">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8283">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8283">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8284">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8284">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8285">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8285">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8286">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8286">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8287">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8287">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8288">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8288">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8289">14 文字の英数字パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8289">14 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8290">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8290">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8291">14 文字の英数字のパターン:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8291">14-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8292">N または n</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8292">N or n</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8293">L または l</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8293">L or l</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8294">オプションのスペース、ドット、またはハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8294">optional space, dot, or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8295">9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8295">nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8296">オプションのスペース、ドット、またはハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8296">optional space, dot, or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8297">B または b</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8297">B or b</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8298">2 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8298">two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8299">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8299">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8300">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8300">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8301">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8301">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8302">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8302">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8303">この関数はFunc_netherlands_value_added_tax_numberパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8303">The function Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8304">検索されたKeywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8304">A keyword from Keywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8305">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8305">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8306">この関数はFunc_netherlands_value_added_tax_numberパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8306">The function Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="4f320d9b-4972-41ae-b337-88d499bb1ade" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="new-zealand-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8315">ニュージーランドの銀行口座番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8315">New Zealand bank account number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8316">この機密情報の種類は、次の場合にのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8316">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8317">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8317">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8318">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8318">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8319">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8319">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8320">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8320">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8321">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8321">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8322">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8322">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8323">14 桁から 16 桁のパターンとオプションの区切り文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8323">14-digit to 16-digit pattern with optional delimiter</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8324">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8324">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8325">14 桁から 16 桁のパターンとオプションの区切り文字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8325">14-digit to 16-digit pattern with optional delimiter:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8326">2 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8326">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8327">任意指定のハイフンまたはスペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8327">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8328">3 ~ 4 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8328">three to four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8329">任意指定のハイフンまたはスペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8329">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8330">7 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8330">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8331">任意指定のハイフンまたはスペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8331">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8332">2 ~ 3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8332">two to three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8333">オプションのハイフンまたはスペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8333">an options hyphen or space</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8334">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8334">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8335">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8335">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8336">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8336">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8337">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8337">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8338">この関数はFunc_new_zealand_bank_account_numberパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8338">The function Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8339">検索されたKeywords_new_zealand_bank_account_number検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8339">A keyword from Keywords_new_zealand_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8340">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8340">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8341">この関数はFunc_new_zealand_bank_account_numberパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8341">The function Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Bank Account Number -->
      <Entity id="1a97fc2b-dd2f-48f1-bc4e-2ddf25813956" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_new_zFealand_bank_account_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="new-zealand-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8349">ニュージーランドの運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8349">New Zealand driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8350">この機密情報の種類は、次の場合にのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8350">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8351">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8351">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8352">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8352">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8353">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8353">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8354">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8354">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8355">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8355">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8356">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8356">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8357">8 文字の英数字パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8357">eight character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8358">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8358">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8359">8 文字の英数字パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8359">eight character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8360">2 文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8360">two letters</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8361">6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8361">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8362">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8362">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8363">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8363">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8364">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8364">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8365">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8365">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8366">この関数はFunc_newzealand_driver_license_numberパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8366">The function Func_newzealand_driver_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8367">検索されたKeywords_newzealand_driver_license_number検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8367">A keyword from Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8368">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたという信頼性が低い。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8368">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8369">この関数はFunc_newzealand_driver_license_numberパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8369">The function Func_newzealand_driver_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Driver License Number -->
      <Entity id="1924b377-d287-49c9-a737-cfe7a8a2615a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
