## <a name="new-zealand-inland-revenue-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8436">ニュージーランドの内陸部の収益番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8436">New Zealand inland revenue number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8437">この機密情報の種類は、次の場合にのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8437">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8438">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8438">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8439">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8439">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8440">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8440">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8441">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8441">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8442">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8442">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8443">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8443">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8444">8 桁または 9 桁の数字とオプションの区切り文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8444">eight or nine digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8445">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8445">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8446">8 桁または 9 桁の数字とオプションの区切り文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8446">eight or nine digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8447">2 桁または 3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8447">two or three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8448">省略可能なスペースまたはハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8448">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8449">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8449">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8450">省略可能なスペースまたはハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8450">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8451">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8451">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8452">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8452">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8453">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8453">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8454">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8454">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8455">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8455">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8456">この関数はFunc_new_zealand_inland_revenue_numberパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8456">The function Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8457">検索されたKeywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8457">A keyword from Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8458">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8458">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8459">この関数はFunc_new_zealand_inland_revenue_numberパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8459">The function Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Inland Revenue Number -->
      <Entity id="dd0fe2bc-7bcf-455f-bac1-83b1e3eb25fd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8460">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8460">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8461">Keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8461">Keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8462">ird no.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8462">ird no.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8463">ird no#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8463">ird no#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8464">nz ird</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8464">nz ird</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8465">ニュージーランド ird</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8465">new zealand ird</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8466">ird number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8466">ird number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8467">内陸部の収益数</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8467">inland revenue number</span></span>


## <a name="new-zealand-ministry-of-health-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8468">ニュージーランド保健省</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8468">New Zealand ministry of health number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8469">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8469">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8470">3 桁の文字、スペース (オプション)、および 4 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8470">three letters, a space (optional), and four digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8471">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8471">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8472">3 文字 (大文字小文字を区別しない) ('I' と 'O' を除く)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8472">three letters (not case-sensitive) except 'I' and 'O'</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8473">スペース (省略可能)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8473">a space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8474">4 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8474">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8475">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8475">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8476">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8476">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8477">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8477">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8478">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8478">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8479">関数 Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8479">The function Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8480">Keyword_nz_terms のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8480">A keyword from Keyword_nz_terms is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8481">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8481">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8482">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8482">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8483">関数 Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8483">The function Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8484">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8484">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- New Zealand Health Number -->
    <Entity id="2b71c1c8-d14e-4430-82dc-fd1ed6bf05c7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_nz_terms" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number" />
       </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="new-zealand-social-welfare-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8498">ニュージーランドのソーシャル ワーカー番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8498">New Zealand social welfare number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8499">この機密情報の種類は、次の場合にのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8499">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8500">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8500">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8501">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8501">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8502">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8502">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8503">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8503">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8504">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8504">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8505">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8505">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8506">9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8506">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8507">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8507">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8508">9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8508">nine digits</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8509">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8509">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8510">オプションのハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8510">an optional hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8511">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8511">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8512">オプションのハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8512">an optional hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8513">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8513">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8514">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8514">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8515">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8515">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8516">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8516">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8517">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8517">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8518">この関数はFunc_newzealand_social_welfare_numberパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8518">The function Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8519">検索されたKeywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8519">A keyword from Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8520">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたという信頼性が低い。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8520">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8521">この関数はFunc_newzealand_social_welfare_numberパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8521">The function Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Newzealand Social Welfare Number -->
      <Entity id="20f3c48d-4ac1-4cd2-86bd-34ecc1826e9d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
    </Version>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8522">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8522">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_new_zealand_social_welfare_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8523">Keyword_new_zealand_social_welfare_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8523">Keyword_new_zealand_social_welfare_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8524">social social sociale#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8524">social welfare #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8525">social social sociale#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8525">social welfare#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8526">social sociale No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8526">social welfare No.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8527">social social sociale number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8527">social welfare number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8528">swn#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8528">swn#</span></span>

   
## <a name="norway-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8529">ノルウェーの識別番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8529">Norway identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8530">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8530">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8531">11 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8531">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8532">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8532">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8533">11 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8533">11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8534">DDMMYY という形式で、生年月日を表す 6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8534">six digits in the format DDMMYY which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8535">3 桁の個人番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8535">three-digit individual number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8536">2 桁のチェック ディジット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8536">two check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8537">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8537">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8538">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8538">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8539">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8539">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8540">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8540">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8541">この関数はFunc_norway_id_numberパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8541">The function Func_norway_id_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8542">検索されたKeyword_norway_id_number検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8542">A keyword from Keyword_norway_id_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8543">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8543">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8544">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8544">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8545">この関数はFunc_norway_id_numbeパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8545">The function Func_norway_id_numbe finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8546">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8546">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Norway Identification Number -->
<Entity id="d4c8a798-e9f2-4bd3-9652-500d24080fc3" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_norway_id_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_norway_id_number"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_norway_id_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8547">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8547">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_norway_id_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8548">Keyword_norway_id_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8548">Keyword_norway_id_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8551">ID Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8551">ID Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8552">Id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8552">Identification</span></span>

## <a name="philippines-unified-multi-purpose-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8555">フィリピンの統一された多目的識別番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8555">Philippines unified multi-purpose identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8556">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8556">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8557">ハイフンで区切られた 12 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8557">12 digits separated by hyphens</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8558">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8558">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8559">12 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8559">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8560">4 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8560">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8561">ハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8561">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8562">7 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8562">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8563">ハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8563">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8564">1 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8564">one digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8565">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8565">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8566">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8566">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8567">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8567">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8568">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8568">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8569">パターンに一Regex_philippines_unified_idコンテンツを検索する正規表現。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8569">The regular expression Regex_philippines_unified_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8570">検索されたKeyword_philippines_id検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8570">A keyword from Keyword_philippines_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Philippines Unified Multi-Purpose ID number -->
<Entity id="019b39dd-8c25-4765-91a3-d9c6baf3c3b3" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_philippines_unified_id"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_philippines_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8571">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8571">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_philippines_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8572">Keyword_philippines_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8572">Keyword_philippines_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8573">Unified Multi-Purpose ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8573">Unified Multi-Purpose ID</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8574">UMID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8574">UMID</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8575">Identity Card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8575">Identity Card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8576">Pinag-isang Multi-Layunin ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8576">Pinag-isang Multi-Layunin ID</span></span>

## <a name="poland-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8577">ポーランドの運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8577">Poland driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8578">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8578">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8579">2 つのスラッシュを含む 14 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8579">14 digits containing two forward slashes</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8580">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8580">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8581">14 桁の数字と 2 つのスラッシュ:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8581">14 digits and two forward slashes:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8582">5 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8582">five digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8583">スラッシュ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8583">a forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8584">2 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8584">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8585">スラッシュ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8585">a forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8586">7 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8586">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8587">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8587">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8588">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8588">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8589">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8589">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8590">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8590">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8591">正規表現は、  `Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8591">The regular expression  `Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8592">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8592">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Poland Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="24d51f99-ee9e-4060-a077-cae58cab1ee4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="poland-identity-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8716">ポーランドの ID カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8716">Poland identity card</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8717">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8717">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8718">3 桁の文字と 6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8718">three letters and six digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8719">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8719">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8720">3 桁の文字 (大文字と小文字を区別しない) の後に 6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8720">three letters (not case-sensitive) followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8721">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8721">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8722">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8722">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8723">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8723">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8724">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8724">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8725">関数 Func_polish_national_id がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8725">The function Func_polish_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8726">Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8726">A keyword from Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8727">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8727">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Poland Identity Card-->
<Entity id="25E64989-ED5D-40CA-A939-6C14183BB7BF" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_national_id" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number" />
      </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8728">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8728">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8729">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8729">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8730">Dowód osobisty</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8730">Dowód osobisty</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8731">Numer dowodu osobistego</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8731">Numer dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8732">Nazwa i numer dowodu osobistego</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8732">Nazwa i numer dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8733">Nazwa i nr dowodu osobistego</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8733">Nazwa i nr dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8734">Nazwa i nr dowodu tożsamości</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8734">Nazwa i nr dowodu tożsamości</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8735">Dowód Tożsamości</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8735">Dowód Tożsamości</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8736">dow.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8736">dow.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8737">os.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8737">os.</span></span>

   
## <a name="poland-national-id-pesel"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8738">ポーランドの国民 ID (PESEL)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8738">Poland national ID (PESEL)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8739">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8739">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8740">11 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8740">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8741">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8741">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8742">YYMMDD の形式で生年月日を表す 6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8742">six digits representing date of birth in the format YYMMDD</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8743">4 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8743">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8744">1 桁のチェック ディジット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8744">one check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8745">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8745">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8746">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8746">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8747">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8747">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8748">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8748">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8749">関数 Func_pesel_identification_number がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8749">The function Func_pesel_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8750">Keyword_pesel_identification_number のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8750">A keyword from Keyword_pesel_identification_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8751">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8751">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8752">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8752">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8753">関数 Func_pesel_identification_number がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8753">The function Func_pesel_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8754">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8754">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Poland National ID (PESEL) -->
      <Entity id="E3AAF206-4297-412F-9E06-BA8487E22456" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_pesel_identification_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_pesel_identification_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_pesel_identification_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8755">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8755">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_pesel_identification_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8756">Keyword_pesel_identification_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8756">Keyword_pesel_identification_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8757">dowód osobisty</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8757">dowód osobisty</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8758">dowódosobisty</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8758">dowódosobisty</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8759">niepowtartartarny numer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8759">niepowtarzalny numer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8760">niepowtartarnynumer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8760">niepowtarzalnynumer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8761">nr.-pesel</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8761">nr.-pesel</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8762">nr-pesel</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8762">nr-pesel</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8763">numer identyfikacyjny</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8763">numer identyfikacyjny</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8764">pesel</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8764">pesel</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8765">to数</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8765">tożsamości narodowej</span></span>

   
## <a name="poland-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8766">ポーランドのパスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8766">Poland passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8767">この機密情報の種類のエンティティは、EU パスポート番号の機密情報の種類に含まれています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8767">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8768">スタンドアロンの機密情報の種類のエンティティとして使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8768">It's available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8769">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8769">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8770">2 桁の文字と 7 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8770">two letters and seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8771">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8771">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8772">2 桁の文字 (大文字と小文字を区別しない) の後に 7 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8772">Two letters (not case-sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8773">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8773">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8774">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8774">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8775">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8775">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8776">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8776">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8777">この関数は `Func_polish_passport_number_v2` 、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8777">The function `Func_polish_passport_number_v2` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8778">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8778">The checksum passes.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8779">キーワードが検出 `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keyword_polish_national_passport_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8779">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keyword_polish_national_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8780">キーワードを `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8780">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8781">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8781">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8782">この関数は `Func_polish_passport_number_v2` 、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8782">The function `Func_polish_passport_number_v2` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8783">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8783">The checksum passes.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8784">キーワードが検出 `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keyword_polish_national_passport_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8784">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keyword_polish_national_passport_number` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8785">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたという信頼性が低い。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8785">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8786">この関数は `Func_polish_passport_number_v2` 、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8786">The function `Func_polish_passport_number_v2` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8787">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8787">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Poland Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="03937FB5-D2B6-4487-B61F-0F8BFF7C3517" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_passport_number_v2" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_passport_number_v2" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_passport_number_v2" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="poland-regon-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8813">ポーランドの REGON 番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8813">Poland REGON number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8814">この機密情報の種類は、次の場合にのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8814">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8815">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8815">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8816">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8816">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8817">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8817">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8818">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8818">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8819">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8819">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8820">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8820">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8821">9 桁または 14 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8821">9-digit or 14-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8822">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8822">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8823">9 桁または 14 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8823">nine digit or 14-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8824">9 桁の数字または</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8824">nine digits or</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8825">9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8825">nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8826">hyphen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8826">hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8827">5 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8827">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8828">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8828">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8829">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8829">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8830">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8830">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8831">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8831">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8832">この関数はFunc_polish_regon_numberパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8832">The function Func_polish_regon_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8833">検索されたKeywords_polish_regon_number検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8833">A keyword from Keywords_polish_regon_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8834">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたという信頼性が低い。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8834">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8835">この関数はFunc_polish_regon_numberパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8835">The function Func_polish_regon_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Polish REGON Number  -->
      <Entity id="fc87b421-f437-4f8b-b739-29a735ead0d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_regon_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_polish_regon_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_regon_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8836">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8836">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_poland_regon_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8837">Keywords_poland_regon_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8837">Keywords_poland_regon_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8838">regon id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8838">regon id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8839">統計数値</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8839">statistical number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8840">統計 ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8840">statistical id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8841">統計なし</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8841">statistical no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8842">regon number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8842">regon number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8843">regonid#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8843">regonid#</span></span>

## <a name="poland-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8852">ポーランドの税識別番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8852">Poland tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8853">この機密情報の種類は、次の場合にのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8853">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8854">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8854">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8855">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8855">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8856">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8856">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8857">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8857">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8858">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8858">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8859">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8859">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8860">11 桁の数字 (スペースまたは区切り記号なし)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8860">11 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8861">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8861">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8862">11 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8862">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8863">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8863">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8864">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8864">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8865">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8865">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8866">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8866">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8867">この関数は  `Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number` 、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8867">The function  `Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8868">キーワードを  `Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number` 検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8868">A keyword from  `Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
  
```xml
      <!-- Poland Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="1ff28b4d-40f2-49e9-b677-9606a88e2bca" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-citizen-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8898">ポルトガルの市民カード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8898">Portugal citizen card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8899">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8899">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8900">8 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8900">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8901">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8901">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8902">8 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8902">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8903">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8903">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8904">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8904">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8905">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8905">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8906">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8906">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8907">パターンに一Regex_portugal_citizen_cardコンテンツを検索する正規表現。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8907">The regular expression Regex_portugal_citizen_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8908">検索されたKeyword_portugal_citizen_card検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8908">A keyword from Keyword_portugal_citizen_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Portugal Citizen Card Number -->
<Entity id="91a7ece2-add4-4986-9a15-c84544d81ecd" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_citizen_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_portugal_citizen_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8928">ポルトガルの運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8928">Portugal driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8929">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8929">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8930">2 つのパターン - 2 文字の後に特殊文字を含む 5 ~ 8 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8930">two patterns - two letters followed by 5-8 digits with special characters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8931">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8931">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8932">パターン 1: 2 文字、その後に特殊文字を含む 5/6。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8932">Pattern 1: Two letters followed by 5/6 with special characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8933">2 文字 (大文字と小文字を区別しない)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8933">Two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8934">ハイフン 1 つ </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8934">A hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8935">5 桁または 6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8935">Five or Six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8936">スペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8936">A space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8937">1 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8937">One digit</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8938">パターン 2: 1 文字の後に特殊文字を含む 6/8 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8938">Pattern 2: One letter followed by 6/8 digits with special characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8939">1 文字 (大文字と小文字を区別しない)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8939">One letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8940">ハイフン 1 つ </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8940">A hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8941">6 桁または 8 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8941">Six or eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8942">スペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8942">A space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8943">1 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8943">One digit</span></span>

    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8944">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8944">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8945">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8945">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8946">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8946">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8947">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8947">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8948">正規表現は、  `Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8948">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8949">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8949">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Portugal Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="977f1e5a-2c33-4bcc-b516-95bb275cff23" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8950">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8950">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-8951">Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-8951">Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number</span></span>

## <a name="portugal-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9081">ポルトガルのパスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9081">Portugal passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9082">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9082">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9083">1 文字の後に 6 桁の数字 (スペースまたは区切り記号なし)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9083">one letter followed by six digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9084">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9084">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9085">1 文字の後に 6 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9085">one letter followed by six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9086">1 文字 (大文字と小文字を区別しない)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9086">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9087">6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9087">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9088">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9088">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9089">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9089">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9090">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9090">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9091">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9091">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9092">正規表現は、  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9092">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9093">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9093">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9094">正規表現が `Regex_eu_passport_date1` DD.MM.YYYY の形式で日付を検出するか、キーワードを `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 検出した</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9094">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9095">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9095">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9096">正規表現は、  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9096">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9097">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9097">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
    
```xml
      <!-- Portugal Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="080a52fd-a7bc-431e-b54d-51f08f59db11" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9124">ポルトガルの税識別番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9124">Portugal tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9125">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9125">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9126">9 桁の数字と省略可能なスペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9126">nine digits with optional spaces</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9127">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9127">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9128">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9128">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9129">省略可能なスペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9129">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9130">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9130">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9131">省略可能なスペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9131">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9132">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9132">three digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9133">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9133">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9134">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9134">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9135">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9135">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9136">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9136">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9137">この関数は  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` 、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9137">The function  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9138">キーワードを  `Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` 検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9138">A keyword from  `Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9139">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたという信頼性が低い。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9139">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9140">この関数は  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` 、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9140">The function  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Portugal Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="65372402-3131-4f1e-9983-4439841d1f15" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="romania-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9165">ルーマニアの運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9165">Romania driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9166">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9166">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9167">1 文字の後に 8 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9167">one character followed by eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9168">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9168">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9169">1 文字の後に 8 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9169">one character followed by eight digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9170">1 文字 (大文字と小文字を区別しない) または数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9170">one letter (not case-sensitive) or digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9171">8 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9171">eight digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9172">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9172">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9173">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9173">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9174">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9174">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9175">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9175">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9176">正規表現は、  `Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9176">The regular expression  `Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9177">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9177">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Romania Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="b5511ace-2fd8-4ae4-b6fc-c7c6e4689e3c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9178">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9178">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9179">Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9179">Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9180">driverlic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9180">driverlic</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9181">driverlics</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9181">driverlics</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9182">driverlicense</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9182">driverlicense</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9183">driverlicenses</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9183">driverlicenses</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9184">driverlicence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9184">driverlicence</span></span>

## <a name="romania-personal-numeric-code-cnp"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9305">ルーマニアの個人数値コード (CNP)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9305">Romania personal numeric code (CNP)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9306">この機密情報の種類は、次の場合にのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9306">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9307">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9307">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9308">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9308">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9309">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9309">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9310">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9310">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9311">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9311">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9312">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9312">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9313">スペースと区切り記号のない 13 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9313">13 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9314">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9314">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9315">1 ~ 9 の 1 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9315">one digit from 1-9</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9316">生年月日 (YYMMDD) を表す 6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9316">six digits representing date of birth (YYMMDD)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9317">2 桁の数字 (01 ~ 52 または 99)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9317">two digits, which can be 01-52 or 99</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9318">4 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9318">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9319">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9319">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9320">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9320">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9321">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9321">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9322">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9322">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9323">この関数は  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` 、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9323">The function  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9324">キーワードを  `Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card` 検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9324">A keyword from  `Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9325">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9325">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9326">この関数は  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` 、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9326">The function  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Romania Personal Numerical Code (CNP) -->
      <Entity id="eb5fa399-fe28-4c67-8188-d63a616ed89c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="romania-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9377">ルーマニアのパスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9377">Romania passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9378">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9378">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9379">スペースと区切り記号のない 8 桁または 9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9379">eight or nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9380">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9380">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9381">8 桁または 9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9381">eight or nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9382">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9382">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9383">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9383">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9384">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9384">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9385">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9385">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9386">正規表現は、  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9386">The regular expression  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9387">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9387">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9388">正規表現が `Regex_romania_eu_passport_date` DD MMM/MMM YY の形式で日付を検出した (例- 01 FEB/FEB 10) またはキーワードが `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 見つかった</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9388">The regular expression `Regex_romania_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD MMM/MMM YY (Example- 01 FEB/FEB 10) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9389">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9389">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9390">正規表現は、  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9390">The regular expression  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9391">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9391">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Romania Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="5d31b90c-7fe2-4a76-a14b-767b8fd19d6c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_romania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_romania_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_romania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9410">この機密情報の種類は、次の場合にのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9410">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9416">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9416">Format</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9418">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9418">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9419">10 桁の数値:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9419">10-digit number:</span></span>
