- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9421">省略可能なスペースまたはハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9421">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9422">2 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9422">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9423">省略可能なスペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9423">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9424">6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9424">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9425">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9425">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9426">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9426">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9427">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9427">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9428">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9428">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9429">正規表現はRegex_Russian_Passport_Number_Domesticパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9429">The regex Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_Domestic finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9430">検索されたKeyword_Russian_Passport_Number検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9430">A keyword from Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Russian Passport Number Domestic -->
      <Entity id="76ec2f5d-cedb-48e1-8070-1998794af445" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_Domestic" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9431">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9431">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9433">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9433">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9434">passport no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9434">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9435">passport#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9435">passport #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9436">passport id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9436">passport id</span></span>

## <a name="russia-passport-number-international"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9447">ロシアのパスポート番号国際番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9447">Russia passport number international</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9448">この機密情報の種類は、次の場合にのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9448">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9449">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9449">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9450">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9450">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9451">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9451">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9452">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9452">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9453">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9453">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9454">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9454">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9455">9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9455">nine-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9456">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9456">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9457">9 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9457">nine-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9458">2 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9458">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9459">省略可能なスペースまたはハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9459">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9460">7 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9460">seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9461">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9461">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9462">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9462">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9463">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9463">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9464">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9464">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9465">正規表現はRegex_Russian_Passport_Number_Internationalパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9465">The regex Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_International finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9466">検索されたKeyword_Russian_Passport_Number検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9466">A keyword from Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Russian Passport Number International -->
      <Entity id="ac5f4878-75e4-4b82-af2d-02e13ea9f411" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_International" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="saudi-arabia-national-id"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9483">サウジアラビアの国民 ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9483">Saudi Arabia National ID</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9484">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9484">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9485">10 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9485">10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9486">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9486">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9487">10 桁の連続する数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9487">10 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9488">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9488">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9489">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9489">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9490">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9490">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9491">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9491">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9492">正規表現 Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9492">The regular expression Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9493">Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9493">A keyword from Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Saudi Arabia National ID -->
<Entity id="8c5a0ba8-404a-41a3-8871-746aa21ee6c0" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9494">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9494">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9495">Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9495">Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9496">Identification Card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9496">Identification Card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9498">ID number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9498">ID number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9499">الوطنية الهوية بطاقة رقم</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9499">الوطنية الهوية بطاقة رقم</span></span> 

   
## <a name="singapore-national-registration-identity-card-nric-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9500">シンガポールの国民登録 ID カード (NRIC) 番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9500">Singapore national registration identity card (NRIC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9501">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9501">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9502">9 桁の文字と数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9502">nine letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9503">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9503">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9504">9 桁の文字と数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9504">nine letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9505">文字 "F"、"G"、"S"、または "T" (大文字小文字を区別しない)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9505">the letter "F", "G", "S", or "T" (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9506">7 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9506">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9507">アルファベットのチェック ディジット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9507">an alphabetic check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9508">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9508">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9509">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9509">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9510">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9510">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9511">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9511">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9512">パターンに一Regex_singapore_nricコンテンツを検索する正規表現。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9512">The regular expression Regex_singapore_nric finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9513">検索されたKeyword_singapore_nric検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9513">A keyword from Keyword_singapore_nric is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9514">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9514">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9515">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9515">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9516">パターンに一Regex_singapore_nricコンテンツを検索する正規表現。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9516">The regular expression Regex_singapore_nric finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9517">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9517">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Singapore National Registration Identity Card (NRIC) Number -->
<Entity id="cead390a-dd83-4856-9751-fb6dc98c34da" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_singapore_nric"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_singapore_nric"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_singapore_nric"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9518">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9518">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_singapore_nric"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9519">Keyword_singapore_nric</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9519">Keyword_singapore_nric</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9520">National Registration Identity Card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9520">National Registration Identity Card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9521">Identity Card Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9521">Identity Card Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9522">NRIC</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9522">NRIC</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9523">IC</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9523">IC</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9524">Foreign Identification Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9524">Foreign Identification Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9525">FIN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9525">FIN</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9526">身份证</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9526">身份证</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9527">身份證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9527">身份證</span></span> 

## <a name="slovakia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9528">スロバキアの運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9528">Slovakia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9529">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9529">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9530">1 文字の後に 7 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9530">one character followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9531">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9531">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9532">1 文字の後に 7 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9532">one character followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9533">1 文字 (大文字と小文字を区別しない) または数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9533">one letter (not case-sensitive) or digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9534">7 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9534">seven digits</span></span> 
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9535">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9535">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9536">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9536">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9537">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9537">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9538">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9538">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9539">正規表現は、  `Regex_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9539">The regular expression  `Regex_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9540">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9540">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovakia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="14240c22-b6de-4ce5-a90b-137f74252513" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="slovakia-personal-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9666">スロバキアの個人番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9666">Slovakia personal number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9667">この機密情報の種類は、次の場合にのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9667">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9668">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9668">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9669">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9669">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9670">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9670">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9671">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9671">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9672">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9672">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9673">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9673">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9674">オプションの円記号を含む 9 桁または 10 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9674">nine or ten digits containing optional backslash</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9675">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9675">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9676">生年月日を表す 6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9676">six digits representing date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9677">オプションのスラッシュ (/)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9677">optional slash (/)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9678">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9678">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9679">オプションのチェック ディジット 1 つ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9679">one optional check digit</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9680">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9680">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9681">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9681">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9682">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9682">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9683">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9683">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9684">この関数は  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` 、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9684">The function  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9685">キーワードを  `Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` 検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9685">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9686">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたという信頼性が低い。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9686">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9687">この関数は  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` 、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9687">The function  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovakia Personal Number -->
      <Entity id="951c26b7-3b35-4f73-924b-15dd599cb9ab" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
    </Version>
```

## <a name="slovakia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9734">スロバキアのパスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9734">Slovakia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9735">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9735">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9736">1 桁の数字または文字の後に 7 桁の数字(スペースまたは区切り文字なし)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9736">one digit or letter followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9737">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9737">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9738">1 桁または文字 (大文字小文字を区別しない) の後に 7 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9738">one digit or letter (not case-sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9739">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9739">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9740">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9740">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9741">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9741">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9742">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9742">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9743">正規表現は、  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9743">The regular expression  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9744">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9744">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9745">正規表現が `Regex_eu_passport_date1` DD.MM.YYYY の形式で日付を検出するか、キーワードを `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 検出した</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9745">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9746">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9746">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9747">正規表現は、  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9747">The regular expression  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9748">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9748">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovakia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="238e1f08-d80e-4793-af33-9b57918335b7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9749">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9749">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9750">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9750">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9751">passport#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9751">passport#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9752">passport#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9752">passport #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9753">passportid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9753">passportid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9754">passports</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9754">passports</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9755">passportno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9755">passportno</span></span>

## <a name="slovenia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9770">スロベニアの運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9770">Slovenia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9771">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9771">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9772">スペースと区切り記号のない 9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9772">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9773">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9773">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9774">9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9774">nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9775">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9775">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9776">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9776">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9777">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9777">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9778">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9778">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9779">正規表現は、  `Regex_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9779">The regular expression  `Regex_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9780">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9780">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="d5bc089a-f2ee-433d-a6b1-5c253051d6f2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="slovenia-unique-master-citizen-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9907">スロベニア固有のマスター市民番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9907">Slovenia Unique Master Citizen Number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9908">この機密情報の種類は、次の場合にのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9908">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9909">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9909">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9910">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9910">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9911">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9911">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9912">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9912">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9913">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9913">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9914">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9914">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9915">13 桁の数字 (スペースまたは区切り記号なし)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9915">13 digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9916">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9916">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9917">指定したパターンの 13 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9917">13 digits in the specified pattern:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9918">生年月日 (DDMMLLL) に対応する 7 桁の数字。"LLL" は生年月日の最後の 3 桁の数字に対応します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9918">seven digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMLLL) where "LLL" corresponds to the last three digits of the birth year</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9919">生年月日の領域 "50" に対応する 2 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9919">two digits that correspond to the area of birth "50"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9920">同じ日に生まれた人の性別とシリアル番号の組み合わせに対応する 3 桁の数字 (男性の場合は 000 ~ 499、女性の場合は 500 ~ 999)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9920">three digits that correspond to a combination of gender and serial number for persons born on the same day (000-499 for male and 500-999 for female)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9921">1 桁のチェック ディジット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9921">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9922">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9922">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9923">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9923">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9924">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9924">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9925">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9925">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9926">この関数は  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` 、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9926">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9927">キーワードを  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` 検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9927">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9928">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9928">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9929">この関数は  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` 、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9929">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Unique Master Citizen Number -->
      <Entity id="68948b27-803d-41e4-adf1-13e05eb541bb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="slovenia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9957">スロベニアのパスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9957">Slovenia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9958">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9958">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9959">2 桁の文字の後に 7 桁の数字 (スペースまたは区切り記号なし)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9959">two letters followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9960">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9960">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9961">2 桁の文字の後に 7 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9961">two letters followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9962">文字 "P"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9962">the letter "P"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9963">1 文字の大文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9963">one uppercase letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9964">7 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9964">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9965">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9965">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9966">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9966">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9967">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9967">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9968">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9968">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9969">正規表現は、  `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9969">The regular expression  `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9970">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9970">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9971">正規表現が `Regex_eu_passport_date1` DD.MM.YYYY の形式で日付を検出するか、キーワードを `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 検出した</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9971">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9972">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9972">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9973">正規表現は、  `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9973">The regular expression  `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9974">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9974">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="235b7976-7bbe-4df5-bb40-08678e749d1a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9975">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9975">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9976">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9976">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9977">passport#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9977">passport#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9978">passport#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9978">passport #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9979">passportid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9979">passportid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9980">passports</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9980">passports</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9981">passportno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9981">passportno</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9982">passport no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9982">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9983">passportnumber</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9983">passportnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9984">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9984">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9985">passportnumbers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9985">passportnumbers</span></span>

## <a name="slovenia-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9997">スロベニアの税金の識別番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9997">Slovenia tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9998">この機密情報の種類は、次の場合にのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9998">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-9999">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-9999">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10000">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10000">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10001">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10001">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10002">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10002">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10003">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10003">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10004">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10004">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10005">スペースまたは区切り記号を含めない 8 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10005">eight digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10006">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10006">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10007">1 ~ 9 の 1 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10007">one digit from 1-9</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10008">6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10008">six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10009">1 桁のチェック ディジット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10009">one check digit</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10010">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10010">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10011">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10011">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10012">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10012">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10013">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10013">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10014">この関数は  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` 、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10014">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10015">キーワードを  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` 検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10015">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10016">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたという信頼性が低い。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10016">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10017">この関数は  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` 、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10017">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="e47b071e-c352-4d70-8241-8c215ad65505" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="south-africa-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10041">南アフリカの識別番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10041">South Africa identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10042">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10042">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10043">省略可能なスペースを含む 13 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10043">13 digits that may contain spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10044">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10044">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10045">13 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10045">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10046">YYMMDD 形式の 6 桁の数字 (生年月日)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10046">six digits in the format YYMMDD, which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10047">4 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10047">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10048">1 桁の市民権インジケーター</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10048">a single-digit citizenship indicator</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10049">数字 "8" または "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10049">the digit "8" or "9"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10050">チェックサム ディジットである 1 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10050">one digit, which is a checksum digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10051">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10051">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10052">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10052">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10053">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10053">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10054">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10054">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10055">この関数はFunc_south_africa_identification_numberパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10055">The function Func_south_africa_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10056">検索されたKeyword_south_africa_identification_number検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10056">A keyword from Keyword_south_africa_identification_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10057">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10057">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- South Africa Identification Number -->
<Entity id="e2adf7cb-8ea6-4048-a2ed-d89eb65f2780" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_south_africa_identification_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_south_africa_identification_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10058">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10058">Keywords</span></span>

## <a name="south-korea-resident-registration-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10063">韓国の住民登録番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10063">South Korea resident registration number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10064">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10064">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10065">ハイフンを 1 つ含む 13 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10065">13 digits containing a hyphen</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10066">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10066">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10067">13 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10067">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10068">YYMMDD 形式の 6 桁の数字 (生年月日)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10068">six digits in the format YYMMDD, which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10069">ハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10069">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10070">1 桁の数字は、年齢と性別によって決まります。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10070">one digit determined by the century and gender</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10071">4 桁の出生地域コード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10071">four-digit region-of-birth code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10072">前の数字が同一の人を区別するために使用される 1 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10072">one digit used to differentiate people for whom the preceding numbers are identical</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10073">チェック ディジット。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10073">a check digit.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10074">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10074">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10075">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10075">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10076">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10076">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10077">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10077">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10078">この関数はFunc_south_korea_resident_numberパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10078">The function Func_south_korea_resident_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10079">検索されたKeyword_south_korea_resident_number検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10079">A keyword from Keyword_south_korea_resident_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10080">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10080">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10081">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10081">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10082">この関数はFunc_south_korea_resident_numberパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10082">The function Func_south_korea_resident_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10083">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10083">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- South Korea Resident Registration Number -->
<Entity id="5b802e18-ba80-44c4-bc83-bf2ad36ae36a" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_south_korea_resident_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_south_korea_resident_number"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_south_korea_resident_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10084">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10084">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_south_korea_resident_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10085">Keyword_south_korea_resident_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10085">Keyword_south_korea_resident_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10086">National ID card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10086">National ID card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10087">Citizen's Registration Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10087">Citizen's Registration Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10088">Jumin deungnok beonho</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10088">Jumin deungnok beonho</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10089">RRN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10089">RRN</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10090">주민등록번호</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10090">주민등록번호</span></span>

## <a name="spain-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10091">スペインの運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10091">Spain driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10092">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10092">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10093">8 桁の数字の後に 1 文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10093">eight digits followed by one character</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10094">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10094">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10095">8 桁の数字の後に 1 文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10095">eight digits followed by one character:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10096">8 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10096">eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10097">1 桁または 1 文字 (大文字と小文字を区別しない)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10097">one digit or letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10098">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10098">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10099">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10099">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10100">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10100">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10101">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10101">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10102">パターンに  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` 一 `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` 致するコンテンツを関数または検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10102">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10103">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10103">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10104">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10104">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10105">パターンに  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` 一 `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` 致するコンテンツを関数または検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10105">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Spain Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="d5a82922-b501-4f40-8868-341321146aa2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="spain-dni"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10239">スペイン DNI</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10239">Spain DNI</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10240">この機密情報の種類は、次の場合にのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10240">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10241">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10241">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10242">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10242">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10243">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10243">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10244">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10244">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10245">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10245">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10246">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10246">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10247">8 桁の数字の後に 1 文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10247">eight digits followed by one character</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10248">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10248">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10249">7 桁の数字の後に 1 文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10249">seven digits followed by one character</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10250">8 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10250">eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10251">省略可能なスペースまたはハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10251">An optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10252">1 つのチェック 文字 (大文字と小文字を区別しない)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10252">one check letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10253">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10253">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10254">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10254">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10255">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10255">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10256">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10256">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10257">パターンに  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` 一 `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` 致するコンテンツを関数または検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10257">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10258">キーワードを  `Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card"` 検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10258">A keyword from  `Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card"` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10259">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10259">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10260">パターンに  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` 一 `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` 致するコンテンツを関数または検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10260">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 

    
```xml
      <!-- Spain DNI -->
      <Entity id="8e6251b9-47b4-40e8-a42b-0f80876be192" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="spain-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10284">スペインのパスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10284">Spain passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10285">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10285">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10286">8 文字または 9 文字の文字と数字の組み合わせ (スペースまたは区切り記号なし)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10286">an eight- or nine-character combination of letters and numbers with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10287">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10287">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10288">文字と数字の 8 文字または 9 文字の組み合わせ:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10288">an eight- or nine-character combination of letters and numbers:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10289">2 桁の数字または文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10289">two digits or letters</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10290">1 桁または 1 文字 (省略可能)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10290">one digit or letter (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10291">6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10291">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10292">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10292">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10293">該当なし</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10293">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10294">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10294">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10295">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10295">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10296">正規表現は、  `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10296">The regular expression  `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10297">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10297">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10298">正規表現が `Regex_spain_eu_passport_date` DD-MM-YYYY の形式で日付を検出するか、キーワードが `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 見つかった</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10298">The regular expression `Regex_spain_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD-MM-YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10299">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10299">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10300">正規表現は、  `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10300">The regular expression  `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10301">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10301">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
    
```xml
      <!-- Spain Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="d17a57de-9fa5-4e9f-85d3-85c26d89686e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_spain_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_spain_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_spain_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10302">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10302">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10303">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10303">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10304">passport#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10304">passport#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10305">passport#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10305">passport #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10306">passportid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10306">passportid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10307">passports</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10307">passports</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10308">passportno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10308">passportno</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10309">passport no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10309">passport no</span></span>

## <a name="spain-social-security-number-ssn"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10330">スペインの社会保障番号 (SSN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10330">Spain social security number (SSN)</span></span>


### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10331">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10331">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10332">11 ～ 12 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10332">11-12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10333">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10333">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10334">11 ~ 12 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10334">11-12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10335">2 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10335">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10336">スラッシュ (省略可能)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10336">a forward slash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10337">7 桁から 8 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10337">seven to eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10338">スラッシュ (省略可能)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10338">a forward slash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10339">2 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10339">two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10340">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10340">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10341">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10341">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10342">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10342">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10343">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10343">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10344">関数 Func_spanish_social_security_number がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10344">The function Func_spanish_social_security_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10345">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10345">The checksum passes.</span></span>
- - <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10346">キーワードを  `Keywords_spain_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10346">A keyword from  `Keywords_spain_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10347">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10347">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10348">関数 Func_spanish_social_security_number がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10348">The function Func_spanish_social_security_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10349">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10349">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- Spain SSN -->
    <Entity id="5df987c0-8eae-4bce-ace7-b316347f3070" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85" relaxProximity="true" >
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spanish_social_security_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spanish_social_security_number" />
        </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```
