## <a name="spain-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10358">スペインの税識別番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10358">Spain tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10359">この機密情報の種類は、次の場合にのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10359">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10360">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10360">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10361">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10361">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10362">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10362">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10363">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10363">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10364">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10364">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10365">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10365">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10366">指定されたパターンの 7 桁または 8 桁の数字と 1 文字または 2 文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10366">seven or eight digits and one or two letters in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10367">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10367">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10368">スペインの国民識別カードを持つスペインの自然人:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10368">Spanish Natural Persons with a Spain National Identity Card:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10369">8 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10369">eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10370">大文字 1 文字 (大文字と小文字を区別)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10370">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10371">スペインの国民識別カードのない非居住者の Spaniards</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10371">Non-resident Spaniards without a Spain National Identity Card</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10372">1 文字の大文字 "L" (大文字と小文字を区別)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10372">one uppercase letter "L" (case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10373">7 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10373">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10374">大文字 1 文字 (大文字と小文字を区別)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10374">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10375">スペインの国民識別カードがない 14 歳未満の住民スペイン人:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10375">Resident Spaniards under the age of 14 years without a Spain National Identity Card:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10376">1 文字の大文字 "K" (大文字と小文字を区別)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10376">one uppercase letter "K" (case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10377">7 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10377">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10378">大文字 1 文字 (大文字と小文字を区別)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10378">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10379">部下の識別番号を持つ部下</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10379">Foreigners with a Foreigner's Identification Number</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10380">"X"、"Y"、または "Z" である 1 つの大文字 (大文字と小文字を区別)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10380">one uppercase letter that is "X", "Y", or "Z" (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10381">7 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10381">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10382">大文字 1 文字 (大文字と小文字を区別)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10382">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10383">子の識別番号を持たなくても</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10383">Foreigners without a Foreigner's Identification Number</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10384">"M" である 1 つの大文字 (大文字と小文字を区別)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10384">one uppercase letter that is "M" (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10385">7 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10385">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10386">大文字 1 文字 (大文字と小文字を区別)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10386">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10387">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10387">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10388">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10388">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10389">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10389">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10390">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10390">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10391">パターンに  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` 一 `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` 致するコンテンツを関数または検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10391">The function  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10392">キーワードを  `Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number` 検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10392">A keyword from  `Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10393">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10393">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10394">パターンに  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` 一 `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` 致するコンテンツを関数または検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10394">The function  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Spain Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="10f0d113-b0e1-47dc-872a-a4f45b9376a3" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10411">税識別番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10411">tax identification number</span></span>

## <a name="sql-server-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10425">SQL Server接続文字列</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10425">SQL Server connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10426">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10426">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10427">文字列 "User Id"、"User ID"、"uid"、または "UserId" の後に、以下のパターンでアウトラインで示されている文字と文字列が続きます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10427">The string "User Id", "User ID", "uid", or "UserId" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10428">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10428">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10429">文字列 "User Id"、"User ID"、"uid"、または "UserId"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10429">the string "User Id", "User ID", "uid", or "UserId"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10430">1 ~ 200 文字の小文字または大文字、数字、記号、特殊文字、またはスペースの任意の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10430">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10431">文字列 "Password" または "pwd" ("pwd" の前に小文字が付いない)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10431">the string "Password" or "pwd" where "pwd" isn't preceded by a lowercase letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10432">等号 (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10432">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10433">ドル記号 ($)、パーセント記号 (%)、記号 (>)、記号 (@)、引用符 (")、セミコロン (;)、左中かっこ([)、または左角かっこ ({) 以外の任意の文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10433">any character that isn't a dollar sign ($), percent symbol (%), greater than symbol (>), at symbol (@), quotation mark ("), semicolon (;), left brace([), or left bracket ({)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10434">セミコロン (;)、スラッシュ (/)、または引用符 (") ではない 7 ~ 128 文字の任意の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10434">any combination of 7-128 characters that are not a semicolon (;), forward slash (/), or quotation mark (")</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10435">セミコロン (;)または引用符 (")</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10435">a semicolon (;) or quotation mark (")</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10436">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10436">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10437">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10437">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10438">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10438">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10439">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10439">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10440">パターンに一CEP_Regex_SQLServerConnectionStringコンテンツを検索する正規表現。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10440">The regular expression CEP_Regex_SQLServerConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10441">指定されたCEP_GlobalFilterが見つかりません。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10441">A keyword from CEP_GlobalFilter isn't found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10442">パターンにCEP_PasswordPlaceHolder一致するコンテンツが見つからない正規表現。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10442">The regular expression CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10443">パターンに一CEP_CommonExampleKeywordsコンテンツが見つからない正規表現。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10443">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```sql
<!---SQL Server Connection String>
<Entity id="e76b6205-d3cb-46f2-bd63-c90153f2f97d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_SQLServerConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_GlobalFilter" />
            <Match idRef="CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder" />
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10444">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10444">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="cep_globalfilter"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10445">CEP_GlobalFilter</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10445">CEP_GlobalFilter</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10446">some-password</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10446">some-password</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10447">somepassword</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10447">somepassword</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10448">secretPassword</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10448">secretPassword</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10449">サンプル</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10449">sample</span></span>

#### <a name="cep_passwordplaceholder"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10450">CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10450">CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10451">(技術的には、この機密情報の種類はキーワード リストではなく正規表現を使用してこれらのキーワードを識別します)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10451">(Note that technically, this sensitive information type identifies these keywords by using a regular expression, not a keyword list.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10452">パスワードまたは pwd の後に 0 ~ 2 スペース、等号 (=)、0 ~ 2 スペース、およびアスタリスク (\*) -OR-</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10452">Password or pwd followed by 0-2 spaces, an equal sign (=), 0-2 spaces, and an asterisk (\*) -OR-</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10453">パスワードまたは pwd の後に次の情報が続きます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10453">Password or pwd followed by:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10454">等号 (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10454">Equal sign (=)</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10455">記号より小さい (<)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10455">Less than symbol (<)</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10456">大文字、小文字、数字、アスタリスク (\*)、ハイフン (-)、下線 (_)、または空白文字の 1 ~ 200 文字の任意の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10456">Any combination of 1-200 characters that are upper- or lowercase letters, digits, an asterisk (\*), hyphen (-), underline (_), or whitespace character</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10457">記号より大きい (>)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10457">Greater than symbol (>)</span></span>

#### <a name="cep_commonexamplekeywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10458">CEP_CommonExampleKeywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10458">CEP_CommonExampleKeywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10459">(技術的には、この機密情報の種類はキーワード リストではなく正規表現を使用してこれらのキーワードを識別します)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10459">(Note that technically, this sensitive information type identifies these keywords by using a regular expression, not a keyword list.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10460">contoso</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10460">contoso</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10461">fabrikam</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10461">fabrikam</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10462">northwind</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10462">northwind</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10463">sandbox</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10463">sandbox</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10464">onebox</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10464">onebox</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10465">localhost</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10465">localhost</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10466">127.0.0.1</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10466">127.0.0.1</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10467">testacs。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10467">testacs.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10468">com</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10468">com</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10469">s-int.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10469">s-int.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10470">net</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10470">net</span></span>

## <a name="sweden-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10471">スウェーデンの運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10471">Sweden driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10472">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10472">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10473">ハイフンを含む 10 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10473">ten digits containing a hyphen</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10474">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10474">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10475">ハイフンを含む 10 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10475">ten digits containing a hyphen:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10476">6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10476">six digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10477">ハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10477">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10478">4 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10478">four digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10479">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10479">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10480">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10480">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10481">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10481">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10482">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10482">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10483">正規表現は、  `Regex_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10483">The regular expression  `Regex_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10484">キーワードが検出  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10484">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Sweden Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="70088720-90dd-47f5-805e-5525f3567391" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="sweden-national-id"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10617">スウェーデンの国民 ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10617">Sweden national ID</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10618">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10618">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10619">10 桁または 12 桁の数字とオプションの区切り記号 1 つ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10619">10 or 12 digits and an optional delimiter</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10620">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10620">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10621">10 桁または 12 桁の数字と省略可能な区切り記号:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10621">10 or 12 digits and an optional delimiter:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10622">2 桁の数字 (省略可能)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10622">two digits (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10623">YYMMDD という日付形式の 6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10623">Six digits in date format YYMMDD</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10624">"-" または "+" の区切り文字 (省略可能)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10624">delimiter of "-" or "+" (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10625">4 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10625">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10626">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10626">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10627">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10627">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10628">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10628">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10629">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10629">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10630">この関数は `Func_swedish_national_identifier` 、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10630">The function `Func_swedish_national_identifier` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10631">キーワード `Keywords_swedish_national_identifier` の検索</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10631">A keyword from `Keywords_swedish_national_identifier` is found</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10632">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10632">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10633">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10633">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10634">この関数は `Func_swedish_national_identifier` 、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10634">The function `Func_swedish_national_identifier` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10635">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10635">The checksum passes.</span></span>


```xml
    <!-- Sweden National ID -->
    <Entity id="f69aaf40-79be-4fac-8f05-fd1910d272c8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_swedish_national_identifier" />
        <Match idRef="Keywords_swedish_national_identifier" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_swedish_national_identifier" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="sweden-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10654">スウェーデンのパスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10654">Sweden passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10655">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10655">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10656">8 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10656">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10657">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10657">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10658">8 桁の連続する数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10658">eight consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10659">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10659">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10660">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10660">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10661">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10661">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10662">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10662">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10663">パターンに一Regex_sweden_passport_numberコンテンツを検索する正規表現。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10663">the regular expression Regex_sweden_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10664">キーワードを検索 `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keyword_sweden_passport` します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10664">a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keyword_sweden_passport` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10665">正規表現は `Regex_sweden_eu_passport_date` 、DD MMM/MMM YY (01 JAN/JAN 12) 形式の日付を検出するか、キーワードを `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 検出します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10665">the regular expression `Regex_sweden_eu_passport_date` finds a date in the format DD MMM/MMM YY (01 JAN/JAN 12) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10666">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10666">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10667">パターンに一Regex_sweden_passport_numberコンテンツを検索する正規表現。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10667">the regular expression Regex_sweden_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10668">キーワードが検出 `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keyword_sweden_passport` された場合。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10668">a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keyword_sweden_passport` is found.</span></span>


```xml
    <!-- Sweden Passport Number -->
    <Entity id="ba4e7456-55a9-4d89-9140-c33673553526" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_sweden_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_sweden_passport" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_sweden_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_sweden_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_sweden_passport" />
          </Any>
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="sweden-social-security-number-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10704">スウェーデンの社会保障番号または同等の識別情報</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10704">Sweden social security number or equivalent identification</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10705">この機密情報の種類のエンティティは、EU 社会保障番号または同等の ID の機密情報の種類でのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10705">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10706">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10706">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10707">スペースと区切り記号のない 12 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10707">12 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10708">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10708">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10709">12 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10709">12 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10710">生年月日に対応する 8 桁の数字 (YYYYMMDD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10710">eight digits that correspond to the birth date (YYYYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10711">シリアル番号に対応する次の 3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10711">three digits that correspond to a serial number where:</span></span> 
  - <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10712">シリアル番号の最後の数字は、男性の奇数と女性の偶数の割り当てによって性別を示します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10712">the last digit in the serial number indicates gender by the assignment of an odd number for male and an even number for female</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10713">1990 年以前は、シリアル番号の割り当ては、番号のベアラーが生まれた郡に対応しました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10713">Before 1990, the assignment of a serial number corresponded to the county where the bearer of the number was born.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10714">または、1947 年 1 月 1 日に、特別なコード (通常は 7 桁目) を持つ税記録に従って、彼らが住んでいる (1947 年以前に生まれた場合)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10714">Or (if born before 1947) where they had been living, according to tax records, on January 1, 1947, with a special code (usually 9 as the seventh digit) for immigrants.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10715">1 桁のチェック ディジット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10715">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10716">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10716">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10717">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10717">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10718">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10718">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10719">DLP ポリシーは、抽出した約 300 文字が次の条件に該当することを検出した場合に、85% の確証を持ってそれがこの種類の機密情報であると特定します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10719">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10720">この関数は  `Func_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10720">The function  `Func_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10721">キーワードを  `Keywords_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10721">A keyword from  `Keywords_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10722">DLP ポリシーは、抽出した約 300 文字が次の条件に該当することを検出した場合に、75% の確証を持ってそれがこの種類の機密情報であると特定します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10722">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10723">この関数は  `Func_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10723">The function  `Func_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU SSN or Equivalent Number -->
<Entity id="d24e32a4-c0bb-4ba8-899d-6303b95742d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern> 
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>      
</Entity>
```

## <a name="sweden-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10739">スウェーデンの税金の識別番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10739">Sweden tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10740">この機密情報の種類は、次の場合にのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10740">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10741">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10741">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10742">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10742">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10743">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10743">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10744">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10744">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10745">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10745">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10746">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10746">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10747">指定されたパターンの 10 桁の数字と記号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10747">10 digits and a symbol in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10748">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10748">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10749">10 桁の数字と記号:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10749">10 digits and a symbol:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10750">生年月日 (YYMMDD) に対応する 6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10750">six digits that correspond to the birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10751">プラス記号または負符号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10751">a plus sign or minus sign</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10752">ID 番号を一意にする 3 桁の数字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10752">three digits that make the identification number unique where:</span></span> 
  - <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10753">1990 年以前に発行された数値の場合、7 番目と 8 番目の数字は出生または外生の人々の郡を示します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10753">for numbers issued before 1990, the seventh and eighth digit identify the county of birth or foreign-born people</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10754">9 番目の位置の数字は、性別が男性の場合は奇数、女性の場合は偶数で示されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10754">the digit in the ninth position indicates gender by either odd for male or even for female</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10755">1 桁のチェック ディジット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10755">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10756">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10756">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10757">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10757">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10758">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10758">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10759">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10759">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10760">この関数は  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` 、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10760">The function  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10761">キーワードを  `Keywords_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` 検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10761">A keyword from  `Keywords_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10762">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10762">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10763">この関数は  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` 、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10763">The function  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Sweden Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="139acba0-a5bc-4fbb-876d-f7a493ae8a40" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="swift-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10789">SWIFT コード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10789">SWIFT code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10790">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10790">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10791">4 文字の後に 5 ~ 31 桁の文字または数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10791">four letters followed by 5-31 letters or digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10792">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10792">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10793">4 文字の後に 5 ~ 31 桁の文字または数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10793">four letters followed by 5-31 letters or digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10794">4 文字の銀行コード (大文字と小文字を区別しない)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10794">four-letter bank code (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10795">省略可能なスペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10795">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10796">4 ～ 28 個の文字または数字 (基本的銀行口座番号 (BBAN))</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10796">4-28 letters or digits (the Basic Bank Account Number (BBAN))</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10797">省略可能なスペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10797">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10798">1 ~ 3 桁の文字または数字 (BBAN の残りの部分)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10798">one to three letters or digits (remainder of the BBAN)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10799">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10799">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10800">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10800">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10801">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10801">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10802">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10802">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10803">正規表現 Regex_swift がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10803">The regular expression Regex_swift finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10804">Keyword_swift のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10804">A keyword from Keyword_swift is found.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="cb2ab58c-9cb8-4c81-baf8-a4e106791df4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_swift" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_swift" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="switzerland-ssn-ahv-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10841">スイスの SSN AHV 番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10841">Switzerland SSN AHV number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10842">この機密情報の種類は、次の場合にのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10842">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10843">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10843">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10844">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10844">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10845">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10845">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10846">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10846">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10847">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10847">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10848">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10848">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10849">13 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10849">13-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10850">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10850">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10851">13 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10851">13-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10852">3 桁の数字 - 756</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10852">three digits - 756</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10853">オプションのドット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10853">an optional dot</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10854">4 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10854">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10855">オプションのドット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10855">an optional dot</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10856">4 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10856">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10857">オプションのドット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10857">an optional dot</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10858">2 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10858">two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10859">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10859">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10860">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10860">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10861">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10861">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10862">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10862">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10863">この関数はFunc_swiss_social_security_number_ahvパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10863">The function Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10864">検索されたKeywords_swiss_social_security_number_ahv検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10864">A keyword from Keywords_swiss_social_security_number_ahv is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10865">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10865">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10866">この関数はFunc_swiss_social_security_number_ahvパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10866">The function Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Swiss SSN AHV Number -->
      <Entity id="277cfa4b-6eaa-4a1b-9492-099dec849971" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_swiss_social_security_number_ahv" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10879">一意の識別なし。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10879">unique identification no.</span></span>

## <a name="taiwan-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10887">台湾の国民識別番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10887">Taiwan national identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10888">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10888">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10889">1 文字 (英語) の後に 9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10889">one letter (in English) followed by nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10890">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10890">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10891">1 文字 (英語) の後に 9 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10891">one letter (in English) followed by nine digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10892">1 文字 (英語、大文字と小文字を区別しない)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10892">one letter (in English, not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10893">数字 "1" または "2"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10893">the digit "1" or "2"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10894">8 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10894">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10895">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10895">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10896">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10896">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10897">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10897">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10898">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10898">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10899">関数 Func_taiwanese_national_id がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10899">The function Func_taiwanese_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10900">Keyword_taiwanese_national_id のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10900">A keyword from Keyword_taiwanese_national_id is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10901">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10901">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10902">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10902">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10903">関数 Func_taiwanese_national_id がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10903">The function Func_taiwanese_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10904">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10904">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwanese National ID -->
<Entity id="4C7BFC34-8DD1-421D-8FB7-6C6182C2AF03" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_taiwanese_national_id" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwanese_national_id" />
      </Pattern>
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
         <IdMatch idRef="Func_taiwanese_national_id" />
       </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10905">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10905">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_taiwan_national_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10906">Keyword_taiwan_national_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10906">Keyword_taiwan_national_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10907">身份證字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10907">身份證字號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10908">身份證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10908">身份證</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10909">身份證號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10909">身份證號碼</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10910">身份證號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10910">身份證號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10911">身分證字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10911">身分證字號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10912">身分證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10912">身分證</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10913">身分證號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10913">身分證號碼</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10914">身份證號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10914">身份證號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10915">身分證統一編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10915">身分證統一編號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10916">國民身分證統一編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10916">國民身分證統一編號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10917">簽名</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10917">簽名</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10918">蓋章</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10918">蓋章</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10919">簽名或蓋章</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10919">簽名或蓋章</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10920">簽章</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10920">簽章</span></span>   
   
## <a name="taiwan-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10921">台湾のパスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10921">Taiwan passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10922">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10922">Format</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10923">生体認証パスポート番号: 9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10923">biometric passport number: nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10924">生体認証以外のパスポート番号: 9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10924">non-biometric passport number: nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10925">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10925">Pattern</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10926">生体認証のパスポート番号:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10926">biometric passport number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10927">文字 "3"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10927">the character "3"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10928">8 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10928">eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10929">生体認証以外のパスポート番号:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10929">non-biometric passport number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10930">9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10930">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10931">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10931">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10932">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10932">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10933">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10933">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10934">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10934">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10935">正規表現はRegex_taiwan_passportパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10935">The regular expression Regex_taiwan_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10936">検索されたKeyword_taiwan_passport検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10936">A keyword from Keyword_taiwan_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwan Passport Number -->
<Entity id="e7251cb4-4c2c-41df-963e-924eb3dae04a" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_taiwan_passport"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwan_passport"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10937">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10937">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_taiwan_passport"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10938">Keyword_taiwan_passport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10938">Keyword_taiwan_passport</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10939">ROC passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10939">ROC passport number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10940">Passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10940">Passport number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10941">Passport no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10941">Passport no</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10942">Passport Num</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10942">Passport Num</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10943">Passport #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10943">Passport #</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10944">护照</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10944">护照</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10945">中華民國護照</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10945">中華民國護照</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10946">Zhōnghuá Mínguó hùzhào</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10946">Zhōnghuá Mínguó hùzhào</span></span>
   
## <a name="taiwan-resident-certificate-arctarc-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10947">台湾の住民証明書 (ARC/TARC) 番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10947">Taiwan-resident certificate (ARC/TARC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10948">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10948">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10949">10 桁の文字と数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10949">10 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10950">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10950">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10951">10 桁の文字と数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10951">10 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10952">2 文字 (大文字と小文字を区別しない)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10952">two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10953">8 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10953">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10954">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10954">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10955">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10955">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10956">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10956">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10957">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10957">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10958">パターンに一Regex_taiwan_resident_certificateコンテンツを検索する正規表現。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10958">The regular expression Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10959">検索されたKeyword_taiwan_resident_certificate検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10959">A keyword from Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwan Resident Certificate (ARC/TARC) -->
<Entity id="48269fec-05ea-46ea-b326-f5623a58c6e9" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10963">Resident Cert</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10963">Resident Cert</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10964">Resident Cert.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10964">Resident Cert.</span></span>

## <a name="thai-population-identification-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10973">タイ語の母集団識別コード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10973">Thai population identification code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10974">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10974">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10975">13 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10975">13 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10976">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10976">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10977">13 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10977">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10978">1 桁目が 0 または 9 ではない</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10978">first digit isn't zero or nine</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10979">12 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10979">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10980">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10980">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10981">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10981">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10982">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10982">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10983">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10983">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10984">この関数はFunc_Thai_Citizen_Idパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10984">The function Func_Thai_Citizen_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10985">検索されたKeyword_Thai_Citizen_Idが見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10985">A keyword from Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10986">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10986">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10987">この関数はFunc_Thai_Citizen_Idパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10987">The function Func_Thai_Citizen_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Thai Citizen ID -->
-<Entity id="44ca9e86-ead7-4c5d-884a-e2eaa401515e" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10988">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10988">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_thai_citizen_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10989">Keyword_thai_citizen_Id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10989">Keyword_thai_citizen_Id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10990">ID 番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10990">ID Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10991">Id 番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10991">Identification Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10992">บัตรประชาชน</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10992">บัตรประชาชน</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10993">รหัสบัตรประชาชน</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10993">รหัสบัตรประชาชน</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10994">บัตรประชาชน</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10994">บัตรประชาชน</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10995">รหัสบัตรประชาชน</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10995">รหัสบัตรประชาชน</span></span>
  
## <a name="turkish-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10996">トルコの国民識別番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10996">Turkish national identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10997">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10997">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10998">11 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10998">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-10999">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-10999">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11000">11 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11000">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11001">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11001">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11002">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11002">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11003">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11003">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11004">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11004">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11005">この関数はFunc_Turkish_National_Idパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11005">The function Func_Turkish_National_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11006">検索されたKeyword_Turkish_National_Id検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11006">A keyword from Keyword_Turkish_National_Id is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11007">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11007">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11008">この関数はFunc_Turkish_National_Idパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11008">The function Func_Turkish_National_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Turkish National Identity -->
-<Entity id="fb621f20-3876-4cfc-acec-8c8e73ca32c7" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Turkish_National_Id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_Turkish_National_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Turkish_National_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11009">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11009">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_turkish_national_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11010">Keyword_turkish_national_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11010">Keyword_turkish_national_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11011">TC Kim tc No</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11011">TC Kimlik No</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11012">TC Kimaras numaras Tc</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11012">TC Kimlik numarası</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11013">Vatandavatl の numaras の数</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11013">Vatandaşlık numarası</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11014">Vatandavatl のいいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11014">Vatandaşlık no</span></span>

## <a name="uk-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11015">英国</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11015">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11016">driver's license number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11016">driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11017">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11017">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11018">指定の形式で組み合わせた 18 桁の文字と数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11018">Combination of 18 letters and digits in the specified format</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11019">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11019">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11020">18 個の文字と数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11020">18 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11021">5 文字 (大文字と小文字を区別しない) または文字の代用の数字 "9" です。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11021">Five letters (not case-sensitive) or the digit "9" in place of a letter.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11022">1 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11022">One digit.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11023">生年月日の日付形式 MMDDY の 5 桁の数字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11023">Five digits in the date format MMDDY for date of birth.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11024">ドライバーが女性の場合、7 番目の文字は 50 ずつ増加します。試験の場合は、01 ~ 12 ではなく 51 ~ 62 です。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11024">The seventh character is incremented by 50 if driver is female; for exampe, 51 to 62 instead of 01 to 12.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11025">2 文字 (大文字と小文字を区別しない) または文字の代用の数字 "9" です。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11025">Two letters (not case-sensitive) or the digit "9" in place of a letter.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11026">5 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11026">Five digits.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11027">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11027">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11028">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11028">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11029">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11029">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11030">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11030">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11031">この関数は `Func_uk_drivers_license` 、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11031">The function `Func_uk_drivers_license` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11032">キーワードを `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` 検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11032">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11033">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11033">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11034">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたという信頼性が低い。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11034">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11035">この関数は `Func_uk_drivers_license` 、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11035">The function `Func_uk_drivers_license` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11036">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11036">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- U.K. Driver's License Number -->
    <Entity id="f93de4be-d94c-40df-a8be-461738047551" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75" relaxProximity="true" >
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_drivers_license" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_drivers_license" />
        </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11052">driverslics</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11052">driverslics</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11053">driverslicence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11053">driverslicence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11054">driverslicences</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11054">driverslicences</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11055">driverslicense</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11055">driverslicense</span></span>
