## <a name="uk-electoral-roll-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11157">英国</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11157">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11158">electoral roll number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11158">electoral roll number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11159">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11159">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11160">2 桁の文字の後に 1 ~ 4 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11160">two letters followed by 1-4 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11161">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11161">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11162">2 文字 (大文字と小文字を区別しない) の後に 1 ~ 4 つの数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11162">two letters (not case-sensitive) followed by 1-4 numbers</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11163">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11163">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11164">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11164">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11165">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11165">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11166">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11166">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11167">正規表現 Regex_uk_electoral がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11167">The regular expression Regex_uk_electoral finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11168">Keyword_uk_electoral のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11168">A keyword from Keyword_uk_electoral is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. Electoral Number -->
<Entity id="a3eea206-dc0c-4f06-9e22-aa1be3059963" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_uk_electoral" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_electoral" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11169">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11169">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_uk_electoral"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11170">Keyword_uk_electoral</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11170">Keyword_uk_electoral</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11171">council nomination</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11171">council nomination</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11172">nomination form</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11172">nomination form</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11173">electoral register</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11173">electoral register</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11174">electoral roll</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11174">electoral roll</span></span>

   
## <a name="uk-national-health-service-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11175">英国</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11175">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11176">national health service number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11176">national health service number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11177">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11177">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11178">スペースで区切られた 10 ～ 17 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11178">10-17 digits separated by spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11179">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11179">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11180">10 ～ 17 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11180">10-17 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11181">3 桁または 10 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11181">either 3 or 10 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11182">スペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11182">a space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11183">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11183">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11184">スペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11184">a space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11185">4 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11185">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11186">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11186">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11187">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11187">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11188">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11188">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11189">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11189">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11190">関数 Func_uk_nhs_number がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11190">The function Func_uk_nhs_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11191">次のいずれかの条件に該当する:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11191">One of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11192">Keyword_uk_nhs_number のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11192">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11193">Keyword_uk_nhs_number1 のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11193">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number1 is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11194">Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11194">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11195">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11195">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. NHS Number -->
<Entity id="3192014e-2a16-44e9-aa69-4b20375c9a78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nhs_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number1" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11196">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11196">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_uk_nhs_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11197">Keyword_uk_nhs_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11197">Keyword_uk_nhs_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11198">national health service</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11198">national health service</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11199">nhs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11199">nhs</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11200">health services authority</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11200">health services authority</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11201">health authority</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11201">health authority</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_uk_nhs_number1"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11202">Keyword_uk_nhs_number1</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11202">Keyword_uk_nhs_number1</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11203">patient id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11203">patient id</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11204">patient identification</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11204">patient identification</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11205">patient no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11205">patient no</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11206">patient number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11206">patient number</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11207">Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11207">Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11208">GP</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11208">GP</span></span>

## <a name="uk-national-insurance-number-nino"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11213">英国</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11213">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11214">国民保険番号 (NINO)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11214">national insurance number (NINO)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11215">この機密情報の種類のエンティティは、EU の国民識別番号の機密情報の種類に含まれています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11215">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11216">スタンドアロンの機密情報の種類のエンティティとして使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11216">It's available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11217">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11217">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11218">スペースまたはダッシュで区切られた 7 文字または 9 文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11218">seven characters or nine characters separated by spaces or dashes</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11219">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11219">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11220">次の 2 つのパターンを使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11220">two possible patterns:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11221">2 文字 (有効な IOS は、このプレフィックスで特定の文字のみを使用します。このパターンでは検証され、大文字と小文字は区別されません)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11221">two letters (valid NINOs use only certain characters in this prefix, which this pattern validates; not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11222">6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11222">six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11223">'A'、'B'、'C'、または 'D' (プレフィックスと同様に、サフィックスでは特定の文字のみ許可され、大文字と小文字は区別されません)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11223">either 'A', 'B', 'C', or 'D' (like the prefix, only certain characters are allowed in the suffix; not case-sensitive)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11224">または</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11224">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11225">2 文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11225">two letters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11226">スペースまたはダッシュ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11226">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11227">2 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11227">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11228">スペースまたはダッシュ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11228">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11229">2 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11229">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11230">スペースまたはダッシュ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11230">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11231">2 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11231">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11232">スペースまたはダッシュ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11232">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11233">'A'、'B'、'C'、または 'D' のいずれか</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11233">either 'A', 'B', 'C', or 'D'</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11234">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11234">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11235">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11235">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11236">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11236">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11237">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11237">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11238">関数 Func_uk_nino がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11238">The function Func_uk_nino finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11239">Keyword_uk_nino のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11239">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nino is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11240">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11240">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11241">関数 Func_uk_nino がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11241">The function Func_uk_nino finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- U.K. NINO -->
    <Entity id="16c07343-c26f-49d2-a987-3daf717e94cc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75" relaxProximity="true">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nino" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nino" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nino" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="uk-unique-taxpayer-reference-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11263">英国</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11263">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11264">一意の納税者参照番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11264">Unique Taxpayer Reference Number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11265">この機密情報の種類は、次の場合にのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11265">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11266">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11266">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11267">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11267">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11268">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11268">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11269">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11269">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11270">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11270">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11271">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11271">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11272">スペースと区切り記号のない 10 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11272">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
 
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11273">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11273">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11274">10 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11274">10 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11275">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11275">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11276">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11276">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11277">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11277">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11278">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11278">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11279">この関数は  `Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number` 、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11279">The function  `Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11280">キーワードを  `Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number` 検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11280">A keyword from  `Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- U.K. Unique Taxpayer Reference Number -->
      <Entity id="ad4a8116-0db8-439a-b545-6d967642f0ec" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11281">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11281">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11282">Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11282">Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11283">tax number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11283">tax number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11285">tax id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11285">tax id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11286">tax identification no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11286">tax identification no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11287">税識別番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11287">tax identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11288">tax no#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11288">tax no#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11289">tax no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11289">tax no</span></span>

## <a name="us-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11300">米国の銀行口座番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11300">U.S. bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11301">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11301">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11302">6 ~ 17 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11302">6-17 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11303">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11303">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11304">6 ~ 17 桁の連続する数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11304">6-17 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11305">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11305">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11306">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11306">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11307">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11307">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11308">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11308">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11309">パターンに一Regex_usa_bank_account_numberコンテンツを検索する正規表現。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11309">The regular expression Regex_usa_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11310">Keyword_usa_Bank_Account のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11310">A keyword from Keyword_usa_Bank_Account is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.S. Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="a2ce32a8-f935-4bb6-8e96-2a5157672e2c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_usa_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_usa_Bank_Account" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="us-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11340">米国の運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11340">U.S. driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11341">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11341">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11342">州に応じて異なる</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11342">Depends on the state</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11343">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11343">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11344">州によって異なります (ニューヨークなど):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11344">depends on the state - for example, New York:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11345">ddd ddd ddd のように書式設定された 9 桁の数字が一致します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11345">nine digits formatted like ddd ddd ddd will match.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11346">dddddd のような 9 桁の数字は一致しません。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11346">nine digits like ddddddddd will not match.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11347">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11347">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11348">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11348">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11349">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11349">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11350">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11350">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11351">関数 Func_new_york_drivers_license_number がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11351">The function Func_new_york_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11352">Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11352">A keyword from Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11353">検索されたKeyword_us_drivers_license検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11353">A keyword from Keyword_us_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11354">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたという信頼性が低い。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11354">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11355">関数 Func_new_york_drivers_license_number がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11355">The function Func_new_york_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11356">Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11356">A keyword from Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11357">Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11357">A keyword from Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11358">Keyword_us_drivers_license のキーワードを検出しなかった。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11358">No keyword from Keyword_us_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="dfeb356f-61cd-459e-bf0f-7c6d28b458c6 patternsProximity="300">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_york_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_new_york_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_us_drivers_license" />
    </Pattern>
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_york_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_new_york_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_us_drivers_license" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="us-individual-taxpayer-identification-number-itin"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11456">米国の個人納税者識別番号 (ITIN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11456">U.S. individual taxpayer identification number (ITIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11457">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11457">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11458">"9" で始まる 9 桁の数字で、4 番目の数字として "7" または "8" が含まれます。必要に応じて、スペースまたはダッシュで書式設定されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11458">nine digits that start with a "9" and contain a "7" or "8" as the fourth digit, optionally formatted with spaces or dashes</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11459">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11459">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11460">書式設定:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11460">formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11461">数字 "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11461">the digit "9"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11462">2 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11462">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11463">スペースまたはダッシュ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11463">a space or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11464">"7" または "8"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11464">a "7" or "8"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11465">1 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11465">a digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11466">スペースまたはダッシュ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11466">a space, or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11467">4 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11467">four digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11468">unformatted:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11468">unformatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11469">数字 "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11469">the digit "9"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11470">2 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11470">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11471">"7" または "8"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11471">a "7" or "8"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11472">5 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11472">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11473">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11473">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11474">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11474">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11475">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11475">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11476">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11476">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11477">関数 Func_formatted_itin がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11477">The function Func_formatted_itin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11478">Keyword_itin のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11478">A keyword from Keyword_itin is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11479">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11479">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11480">関数 Func_unformatted_itin がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11480">The function Func_unformatted_itin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11481">Keyword_itin のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11481">A keyword from Keyword_itin is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11482">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたという信頼性が低い。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11482">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11483">この関数はFunc_formatted_itinまたはFunc_unformatted_itinパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11483">The function Func_formatted_itin or Func_unformatted_itin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- U.S. Individual Taxpayer Identification Number (ITIN) -->
    <Entity id="e55e2a32-f92d-4985-a35d-a0b269eb687b" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_formatted_itin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_itin" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_itin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_itin" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_formatted_itin" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_itin" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11484">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11484">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_itin"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11485">Keyword_itin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11485">Keyword_itin</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11486">taxpayer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11486">taxpayer</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11487">tax id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11487">tax id</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11488">tax identification</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11488">tax identification</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11489">itin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11489">itin</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11490">i.t.i.n.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11490">i.t.i.n.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11491">ssn</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11491">ssn</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11492">tin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11492">tin</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11493">social security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11493">social security</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11494">tax payer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11494">tax payer</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11495">itins</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11495">itins</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11496">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11496">taxid</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11497">individual taxpayer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11497">individual taxpayer</span></span> 


## <a name="us-social-security-number-ssn"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11498">米国の社会保障番号 (SSN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11498">U.S. social security number (SSN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11499">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11499">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11500">9 桁の数字(書式設定されたパターンまたは書式設定されていないパターンの場合があります)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11500">nine digits, which may be in a formatted or unformatted pattern</span></span>

> [!NOTE]
> <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11501">2011 年半ばより前に発行された場合、SSN には強力な書式が設定されています。この書式では、数値の特定の部分が有効な範囲内に含む必要があります (チェックサムはありません)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11501">If issued before mid-2011, an SSN has strong formatting where certain parts of the number must fall within certain ranges to be valid (but there's no checksum).</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11502">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11502">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11503">4 つの関数は、4 つの異なるパターンで SSN を探します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11503">four functions look for SSNs in four different patterns:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11504">Func_ssn は、2011 年以前の厳密な書式の SSN を検索します。これはダッシュまたはスペース (ddd-dd-dddd または ddd dd dddd) の形式になっています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11504">Func_ssn finds SSNs with pre-2011 strong formatting that are formatted with dashes or spaces (ddd-dd-dddd OR ddd dd dddd)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11505">Func_unformatted_ssn は、2011 年以前の厳密な書式の SSN を検索します。これは 9 桁の連続した数字 (ddddddddd) の形式になっています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11505">Func_unformatted_ssn finds SSNs with pre-2011 strong formatting that are unformatted as nine consecutive digits (ddddddddd)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11506">Func_randomized_formatted_ssn は、2011 年以降の SSN を検索します。これはダッシュまたはスペース (ddd-dd-dddd または ddd dd dddd) の形式になっています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11506">Func_randomized_formatted_ssn finds post-2011 SSNs that are formatted with dashes or spaces (ddd-dd-dddd OR ddd dd dddd)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11507">Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn は、2011 年以降の SSN を検索します。これは 9 桁の連続した数字 (ddddddddd) の形式になっています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11507">Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn finds post-2011 SSNs that are unformatted as nine consecutive digits (ddddddddd)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11508">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11508">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11509">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11509">No</span></span>


### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11510">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11510">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11511">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11511">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11512">関数 Func_ssn がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11512">The function Func_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11513">Keyword_ssn のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11513">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11514">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11514">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11515">この関数はFunc_unformatted_ssnパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11515">The function Func_unformatted_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11516">Keyword_ssn のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11516">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11517">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたという信頼性が低い。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11517">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11518">関数 Func_randomized_formatted_ssn がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11518">The function Func_randomized_formatted_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11519">Keyword_ssn のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11519">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11520">DLP ポリシーは、抽出した約 300 文字が次の条件に該当することを検出した場合に 55% の確証を持ってそれがこの種類の機密情報であると特定します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11520">A DLP policy is 55% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11521">関数 Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11521">The function Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11522">Keyword_ssn のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11522">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>


```xml
<!-- U.S. Social Security Number (SSN) -->
  <Entity id="a44669fe-0d48-453d-a9b1-2cc83f2cba77" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_randomized_formatted_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="55">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
  </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11527">社会保障#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11527">social security #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11528">社会保障#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11528">social security#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11529">社会保障なし</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11529">social security no</span></span>

## <a name="us--uk-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11537">米国/英国</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11537">U.S. / U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11538">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11538">passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11539">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11539">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11540">9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11540">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11541">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11541">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11542">9 桁の連続する数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11542">nine consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11543">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11543">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11544">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11544">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11545">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11545">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11546">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合に、この種の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11546">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11547">関数 Func_usa_uk_passport がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11547">The function Func_usa_uk_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11548">キーワードが検出 `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_uk_eu_passport_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11548">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_uk_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11549">キーワード `Keywords_eu_passport_date` の検索</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11549">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11550">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11550">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11551">関数 Func_usa_uk_passport がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11551">The function Func_usa_uk_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11552">キーワードが検出 `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_uk_eu_passport_number` された、または検出された。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11552">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_uk_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- U.S. / U.K. Passport Number -->
    <Entity id="178ec42a-18b4-47cc-85c7-d62c92fd67f8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_usa_uk_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_uk_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_usa_uk_passport" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_uk_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11556">passport#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11556">passport #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11557">passportid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11557">passportid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11558">passports</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11558">passports</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11559">passportno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11559">passportno</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11562">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11562">passport number</span></span>

## <a name="ukraine-passport-domestic"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11568">ウクライナのパスポート(国内)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11568">Ukraine passport domestic</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11569">この機密情報の種類は、次の場合にのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11569">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11570">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11570">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11571">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11571">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11572">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11572">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11573">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11573">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11574">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11574">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11575">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11575">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11576">9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11576">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11577">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11577">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11578">9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11578">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11579">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11579">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11580">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11580">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11581">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11581">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11582">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11582">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11583">正規表現はRegex_Ukraine_Passport_Domesticパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11583">The regex Regex_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11584">検索されたKeyword_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11584">A keyword from Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Ukraine Passport Domestic -->
      <Entity id="1817a540-221f-4459-9202-3bd78b81d803" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic"/>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11585">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11585">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_ukraine_passport_domestic"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11586">Keyword_ukraine_passport_domestic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11586">Keyword_ukraine_passport_domestic</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11587">passport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11587">ukraine passport</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11588">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11588">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11589">passport no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11589">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11590">паспорт України</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11590">паспорт України</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11591">номер паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11591">номер паспорта</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11592">персональний</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11592">персональний</span></span>


## <a name="ukraine-passport-international"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11593">ウクライナのパスポート国際</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11593">Ukraine passport international</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11594">この機密情報の種類は、次の場合にのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11594">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11595">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11595">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11596">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11596">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11597">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11597">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11598">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11598">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11599">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11599">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11600">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11600">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11601">8 文字の英数字パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11601">eight-character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11602">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11602">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11603">8 文字の英数字のパターン:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11603">eight-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11604">2 桁の文字または数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11604">two letters or digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11605">6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11605">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11606">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11606">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11607">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11607">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11608">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11608">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11609">DLP ポリシーは、約 300 文字以下の場合にこの種の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼度を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11609">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11610">正規表現はRegex_Ukraine_Passport_Internationalパターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11610">The regex Regex_Ukraine_Passport_International finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="c2bb0-11611">検索されたKeyword_Ukraine_Passport_International検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2bb0-11611">A keyword from Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_International is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Ukraine Passport International -->
      <Entity id="cfbe032d-22e0-4f28-ab68-d66e9641f1e2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Ukraine_Passport_International"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_International"/>
        </Pattern>
```
